%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20a%20peace%20deal%20with%20Iran%20won't%20save%20the%20economy%20from%20energy-market%20chaos%20this%20summer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224562%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Oil%20tanker%20crossing%20the%20sea%20at%20sunset%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb70595edd94d1e7339d21%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223042%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERonen%20Tivony%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAn%20Iran%20peace%20deal%20won't%20be%20an%20quick%20fix%20for%20fuel%20shortages%20and%20high%20oil%20prices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMarket%20distortions%20will%20still%20impact%20the%20economy%20even%20if%20a%20peace%20deal%20is%20finalized%20soon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECrude%20reserves%20will%20likely%20be%20depleted%20right%20as%20summer%20begins%2C%20according%20to%20some%20forecasts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-war-peace-deal-oil-prices-us-stocks-tech-rally-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUS-Iran%20peace%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20be%20close%2C%20but%20relief%20from%20the%20disruptions%20caused%20by%20the%20conflict%20is%20a%20more%20distant%20reality.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20idea%20that%20the%20conflict's%20end%20might%20be%20not%20be%20a%20quick%20fix%20for%20the%20energy%20market%20hasn't%20been%20digested%20yet%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcommodities%2Foil-price-today-crude-drops-report-us-iran-peace-deal-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoil%20prices%20plunging%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Wednesday%20on%20news%20that%20a%20deal%20was%20at%20hand.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20cheered%20a%20report%20from%20Axios%20that%20said%20the%20US%20and%20Iran%20were%20nearing%20a%20resolution%20that%20could%20end%20the%20war%2C%20and%2C%20importantly%2C%20reopen%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-to-invest-iran-war-strait-of-hormuz-stock-market-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EStrait%20of%20Hormuz%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20oil%20flowing%20to%20the%20world%20again.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20notion%20that%20oil%20markets%20will%20revert%20back%20to%20normal%20once%20the%20war%20ends%20is%20unrealistic%2C%20according%20to%20energy%20experts%2C%20who%20are%20eyeing%20at%20least%20several%20months%20after%20the%20end%20of%20the%20war%20before%20crude%20markets%20will%20normalize.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20that%20means%20almost%20nothing%20can%20stop%20the%20economy%20from%20feeling%20the%20impacts%20of%20depleted%20reserves%2C%20critical%20fuel%20shortages%2C%20and%20high%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeff%20Currie%2C%20a%20longtime%20commodities%20analyst%20and%20the%20chief%20strategy%20officer%20of%20Energy%20Pathways%20at%20Carlyle%2C%20said%20he%20believes%20much%20of%20the%20damage%20the%20war%20has%20inflicted%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-supply-shock-outlook-breaking-point-global-crude-supply-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoil%20markets%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20be%20felt%20in%20the%20medium-term.%20Speaking%20to%20Bloomberg%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20he%20pointed%20to%20how%20shippers%20and%20insurers%20need%20to%20regain%20confidence%20that%20traveling%20in%20the%20Strait%20is%20safe%20again%20before%20starting%20to%20reconfigure%20ship%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20three%20months%20bare%20minimum%2C%26quot%3B%20Currie%20said%20of%20the%20lasting%20impact%20of%20the%20war%2C%20despite%20oil%20prices%20tumbling%20lower%20in%20the%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22270bb966-4ed2-4c38-8e0f-96fa9076eeaf%5C%22%3ETrue%20supply%20shortages%20will%20hit%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECurrie%20said%20the%20current%20supply%20situation%20in%20the%20US%20and%20Europe%20is%20an%20oil%20deficit%20as%20opposed%20to%20an%20actual%20shortage%2C%20since%20nations%20are%20drawing%20on%20oil%20reserves.%20Once%20reserves%20run%20out%2C%20true%20oil%20shortages%20will%20begin%2C%20he%20said%2C%20speculating%20that%20distillate%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-much-surging-jet-fuel-prices-have-cost-us-airlines-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejet%20fuel%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20likely%20be%20the%20first%20crude%20byproducts%20to%20run%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20baked%20in%2C%20full%20stop%2C%26quot%3B%20Currie%20said%20of%20coming%20fuel%20shortages%2C%20even%20if%20the%20war%20were%20to%20end%20today.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20take%20so%20long%20to%20get%20all%20this%20restarted%20that%20those%20inventories%20will%20continue%20to%20draw.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurrie%20said%20oil%20stores%20were%20already%20being%20depleted%20in%20pockets%20of%20Asia.%20Stores%20will%20likely%20hit%20%26quot%3Btank%20bottoms%26quot%3B%20in%20Europe%20in%20May%2C%20while%20the%20US%20will%20likely%20run%20out%20of%20its%20reserves%20by%20the%20fourth%20of%20July%2C%20he%20estimated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHFI%20Research%2C%20an%20investment%20research%20firm%20specializing%20in%20energy%2C%20said%20it%20also%20anticipates%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-price-outlook-iran-war-supply-shortage-hoarding-panic-buying-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshortages%20to%20hit%20the%20global%20economy%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20coming%20months.%20In%20a%20recent%20note%2C%20the%20firm%20predicted%20that%20the%20US%20could%20run%20out%20of%20%26quot%3Bbuffer%26quot%3B%20crude%20product%20stores%20in%20two%20weeks%2C%20while%20buffer%20oil%20stores%20could%20run%20out%20in%20eight%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EForecasters%20are%20particularly%20concerned%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-oil-jet-fuel-naphtha-lpg-shortage-hormuz-disruption-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoutlook%20for%20fuel%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChristopher%20Hodge%2C%20chief%20US%20economist%20at%20Natixis%20CIB%20Americas%2C%20noted%20that%20while%20a%20jet%20fuel%20shortage%20would%20be%20highly%20inflationary%20for%20all%20aviation-exposed%20sectors%20in%20the%20short%20term.%20However%2C%20he%20added%20that%20the%20broader%20consequences%20likely%20won't%20be%20confined%20to%20the%20travel%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHouseholds%20paying%20more%20for%20airfare%2C%20gasoline%2C%20or%20delivered%20goods%20have%20less%20income%20to%20spend%20elsewhere%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThat%20means%20discretionary%20categories%2C%20restaurants%2C%20leisure%2C%20retail%20goods%2C%20entertainment%2C%20and%20nonessential%20services%2C%20could%20see%20softer%20demand%20and%20weaker%20pricing%20power%20over%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrett%20Massimino%2C%20department%20chair%20supply%20chain%20management%20at%20Virginia%20Commonwealth%20University%2C%20added%20that%20other%20areas%20of%20transportation%20that%20are%20already%20under%20pressure%20could%20be%20further%20impacted%20by%20a%20jet%20fuel%20shortage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20already%20seeing%20diesel%20prices%20at%20%246.00%20or%20more%20per%20gallon%20in%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BHigher%20diesel%20prices%20work%20their%20way%20into%20nearly%20every%20product%20a%20consumer%20buys%2C%20as%20it's%20a%20vital%20component%20of%20the%20agriculture%2C%20production%2C%20and%20transportation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman%20Sachs%20said%20it%20believed%20European%20commercial%20jet%20fuel%20inventories%20could%20fall%20by%20the%20International%20Energy%20Agency's%20key%2023-day%20threshold%20by%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairlines-cutting-most-flights-summer-chart-graph-spirit-united-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMore%20flights%20are%20likely%20to%20get%20canceled%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20jet%20fuel%20runs%20low%2C%20HFI%20said%20in%20a%20note.%20HFI%20Founder%20Wilson%20Wang%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20final%20economic%20impact%20depends%20on%20how%20many%20carriers%20slash%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMatt%20Smith%2C%20the%20director%20of%20commodity%20research%20at%20Kpler%2C%20said%20he%20was%20also%20concerned%20about%20flight%20cancellations%20through%20the%20summer%20travel%20season%20as%20fuel%20stores%20dwindle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJet%20is%20the%20first%20one%20to%20go.%20Asia%20is%20the%20first%20region%2C%20but%20it's%20going%20to%20spread%20across%20the%20globe%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20speaking%20to%20CNBC%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22441acc8f-6dd8-4918-ae11-8aeb6968b87c%5C%22%3EHigher%20prices%20will%20be%20here%20for%20a%20while%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcommodities%2Foil-price%3Ftype%3Dwti%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOil%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20likely%20to%20stay%20well%20above%20pre-war%20levels%20for%20some%20time.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrent%20crude%2C%20the%20international%20benchmark%2C%20tumbled%20as%20much%20as%209%25%20in%20the%20early%20morning%20to%20%2497%20a%20barrel%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20but%20crept%20back%20above%20%24100%20line%20later%20in%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHFI%20predicted%20there%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bripple%20effect%26quot%3B%20in%20oil%20markets%20as%20the%20supply%20shortage%20triggers%20panic%20buying%20in%20areas%20like%20Asia.%20Increased%20demand%20will%20raise%20oil%20prices%2C%20which%20will%20raise%20profit%20margins%20for%20refiners.%20That%20will%20further%20stoke%20oil%20demand%20and%20raise%20prices%2C%20the%20firm%20speculated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20said%20it%20saw%20oil%20prices%20surpassing%20their%202008%20peak%20to%20top%20%24150%20a%20barrel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20Whalen%2C%20a%20longtime%20analyst%20and%20the%20chairman%20of%20Whalen%20Global%20Advisors%2C%20recently%20told%20BI%20he%20believed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Firan-war-inflation-shock-oil-prices-us-economy-outlook-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einflationary%20impacts%20of%20higher%20oil%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20likely%20stick%20around%20for%20years%20to%20come%2C%20even%20if%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20were%20to%20open%20shop%20tomorrow.%20He%20pointed%20to%20how%20shipping%20has%20been%20severely%20disrupted%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20fact%20that%20energy%20infrastructure%20that's%20been%20destroyed%20in%20the%20region%20will%20take%20years%20to%20rebuild.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20talking%20about%20months%20or%20years%2C%20depending%20on%20how%20much%20damage%2C%26quot%3B%20Whalen%20said%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-supply-outlook-fuel-shortage-crude-prices-iran-war-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778145602000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb7064f9e4752b6d60169c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-supply-outlook-fuel-shortage-crude-prices-iran-war-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Oil%20markets%20will%20likely%20remain%20distorted%20for%20months%20after%20the%20Iran%20war%20ends%2C%20leading%20reserves%20to%20dwindle%20to%20critical%20levels.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jsor%40businessinsider.com%20(Jennifer%20Sor%2CSamuel%20O'Brient)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20thought%20living%20in%20a%20retirement%20community%20in%20my%2070s%20might%20mean%20slowing%20down.%20I%20was%20very%2C%20very%20wrong.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20lives%20with%20her%20husband.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb7c2ae1443b8dc48e26c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOnce%20hesitant%20to%20move%20into%20a%20retirement%20community%2C%20the%20author%20said%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20have%20enjoyed%20trying%20the%20many%20different%20amenities%20their%20new%20home%20offers.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Maureen%20Rubin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20were%20craving%20more%20space%20and%20amenities%20to%20fill%20our%20time%20with%20in%20our%20retirement.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20hesitated%20to%20consider%20a%20retirement%20community%2C%20fearing%20dull%2C%20elderly%20neighbors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20new%20life%20is%20filled%20with%20vibrant%2C%20interesting%20people.%20I'm%20so%20glad%20I%20considered%20this%20lifestyle.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20cooped%20up%20in%20our%20two-bedroom%20condominium%20for%20nearly%20two%20years%20during%20COVID%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-boomers-moved-into-bigger-home-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecraved%20space%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuperager-father-still-works-no-plans-to-retire-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretired%20professionals%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20our%2070s%2C%20we%20considered%20moving%20to%20a%20retirement%20community%20with%20lots%20of%20amenities%20for%20us%20to%20enjoy.%20But%20we%20both%20feared%20it%20would%20be%20full%20of%20feeble%2C%20old%2C%20boring%20people.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20so%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f8e32a7e-b668-46c5-a54f-851b0e5cd81a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20found%20a%20place%20worth%20checking%20out%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20my%20husband%20of%2045%20years%20(48%20now)%20and%20I%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworst-things-about-living-in-la-california-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eliving%20in%20Los%20Angeles%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20knew%20we%20wanted%20to%20stay%20in%20California%2C%20but%20craved%20a%20spot%20without%20the%20crowds%20and%20traffic.%20We%20hoped%20to%20be%20near%20a%20golf%20course%20and%20around%20interesting%20people%20and%20fun%20activities.%20Was%20that%20possible%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20Googled%20%26quot%3Bretirement%20communities%26quot%3B%20and%20immediately%20rejected%20places%20too%20far%20north%20or%20too%20far%20south.%20We%20found%20a%20place%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmonterey-california-best-things-to-do-from-local-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eon%20the%20Central%20Coast%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20fit%20our%20requirements.%20It%20was%20near%20San%20Luis%20Obispo%2C%20a%20college%20town%20with%20cool%20stores%20and%20restaurants.%20It%20was%20on%20a%20golf%20course%2C%20had%20a%20community%20center%2C%20and%20offered%20pickleball%2C%20tennis%2C%20quilting%2C%20Zumba%2C%20aqua%20aerobics%2C%20Pilates%2C%20mahjong%2C%20pottery%2C%20and%20yoga%20on%20a%20typical%20day.%20What%20more%20could%20we%20need%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20husband%20swings%20a%20golf%20club.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb7cade1443b8dc48e26d2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20were%20looking%20for%20a%20location%20that%20offered%20more%20space%2C%20less%20traffic%2C%20and%20easy%20access%20to%20activities%20like%20golf.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Maureen%20Rubin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20told%20that%20evenings%20would%20be%20filled%20with%20happy%20hours%20with%20music%2C%20comedians%2C%20or%20lectures%2C%20and%20that%20they%20often%20hosted%20outdoor%20dances%20with%20live%20bands.%20There%20was%20also%20lots%20of%20wine%20tasting%2C%20since%20the%20community%20is%20so%20close%20to%20many%20wineries.%20We%20wanted%20to%20sample%20them%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d4f52e65-b415-40b6-8598-fbd2cf3bfb4f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20community%20was%20lovely%2C%20but%20we%20were%20still%20hesitant%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20we%20were%20skeptical%20about%20our%20potential%20neighbors%2C%20but%20we%20decided%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try%20and%20signed%20a%20lease%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckily%2C%20our%20worries%20were%20short-lived.%20While%20the%20workers%20were%20still%20unloading%20boxes%20from%20the%20moving%20vans%2C%20Linda%2C%20a%20woman%20who%20lived%20on%20our%20block%2C%20knocked%20on%20our%20door%20and%20introduced%20herself.%20She%20invited%20us%20over%20for%20wine%20(I%20told%20you)%20and%20cheese%2C%20so%20we%20could%20meet%20her%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20lived%20next%20door%20to%20several%20people%20in%20Los%20Angeles%20for%20years%20and%20never%20even%20met%20them%2C%20but%20now%20I%20was%20meeting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthought-too-old-make-new-friends-bold-move-proved-wrong-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epotential%20new%20friends%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20our%20first%20day%20in%20the%20neighborhood.%20This%20was%20unexpected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinda's%20meet-and-greet%20reminded%20us%20of%20our%20freshman%20year%20in%20college%2C%20where%20everyone%20is%20a%20little%20anxious%20to%20make%20new%20friends%20and%20try%20new%20things.%20My%20neighbors%20assured%20me%20that%20if%20I%20attended%20activities%20I%20enjoyed%2C%20I%20was%20sure%20to%20meet%20people%20with%20similar%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Linda's%20guests%20was%20a%20retired%20dentist%20who%20became%20a%20certified%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-zumba-became-the-largest-fitness-brand-in-the-world-2012-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EZumba%20instructor%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20she%20stopped%20drilling%20teeth.%20Another%20invited%20me%20to%20join%20her%20book%20club%2C%20where%20I%20immediately%20bonded%20with%20other%20literature%20lovers.%20A%20different%20guest%20asked%20me%20if%20I%20wanted%20to%20join%20her%20gourmet%20cooking%20class.%20A%20fourth%2C%20who%20told%20us%20she%20used%20to%20be%20in%20the%20CIA%2C%20was%20starting%20a%20program%20to%20discuss%20current%20foreign%20policy%20issues%20each%20week%20and%20wanted%20to%20know%20if%20we%20would%20like%20to%20join.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22992e5dbb-6f7d-47f0-a839-bbd81d9096d7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20found%20out%20the%20community%20likes%20to%20give%20back%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20impressed%20by%20my%20new%20friends'%20commitment%20to%20giving%20back%20to%20their%20community%2C%20too.%20I%20found%20out%20that%20some%20neighbors%20tutored%20kids%20and%20gathered%20healthy%20food%20and%20clothes%20for%20low-income%20families.%20Others%20donated%20toys%20and%20prepared%20special%20meals%20for%20those%20in%20need.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20pledged%20to%20help%20out%20where%20we%20could.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20to%20realize%20that%20in%20our%20new%20home%2C%20we%20were%20surrounded%20by%20kind%2C%20friendly%2C%20like-minded%20people.%20We%20felt%20like%20we%20had%20won%20the%20retirement%20lottery.%20This%20community%20had%20not%20only%20what%20we%20were%20looking%20for%2C%20but%20was%20loaded%20with%20benefits%20we%20never%20even%20thought%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c874643-751a-4ca5-bbac-bab915266b64%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20trying%20new%20things%2C%20and%20enjoying%20some%20of%20them%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20not%20successful%20at%20everything%20I%20tried%20in%20my%20new%20community.%20I%20took%20a%20pottery%20class%2C%20and%20my%20vase%20turned%20out%20lopsided%20and%20just%20plain%20ugly.%20After%20completing%20a%20beginner%20jewelry-making%20class%2C%20my%20fellow%20classmates%20headed%20to%20the%20intermediate%E2%80%94level%20class.%20The%20teacher%20suggested%20that%20I%20might%20want%20to%20repeat%20the%20beginner%20class.%20I%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20(right)%20enjoys%20a%20Zumba%20class%20that%20takes%20place%20iin%20the%20community%20she%20lives%20in.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb7d23c9dd4cb81cda7bfb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20(right)%20said%20that%20she%20hasn't%20taken%20to%20all%20of%20the%20activities%20offered%20%E2%80%94%20pottery%20and%20jewelry-making%20weren't%20wins%20%E2%80%94%20but%20admits%20she%20has%20enjoyed%20regular%20Zumba%20classes.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Maureen%20Rubin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20like%20water%20aerobics%20because%20the%20water%20was%20freezing.%20And%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretired-health-issues-second-career-pickleball-coach-aging-longevity-purpose-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epickleball%20game%3C%2Fa%3E%20left%20me%20terrified%20of%20breaking%20an%20ankle%20or%20a%20hip.%20But%20there%20were%20so%20many%20other%20options%2C%20I%20didn't%20mind%20narrowing%20my%20scope.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20I've%20learned%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-worst-cities-for-retirees-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretirement%20communities%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecan%20be%20a%20great%2C%20fun%2C%20and%20productive%20way%20to%20spend%20your%20senior%20years.%20I%20can't%20speak%20for%20all%20of%20them%2C%20but%20in%20mine%2C%20there%20are%20no%20toddering%20old%20bores.%20Instead%2C%20I'm%20surrounded%20by%20tons%20of%20vibrant%2C%20interesting%2C%20caring%2C%20and%20active%20people%2C%20and%20loads%20of%20things%20to%20do.%20I'm%20so%20glad%20I%20came%20around%20to%20this%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20been%20here%20three%20and%20a%20half%20years%20now%2C%20and%20we%20love%20it.%20We%20tell%20our%20LA%20friends%20and%20our%20kids%20about%20it%2C%20but%20most%20of%20them%20remain%20skeptical.%20That's%20their%20loss!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffeared-retirement-community-life-better-than-expected-independent-living-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778145601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb7c2ae1443b8dc48e26c5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffeared-retirement-community-life-better-than-expected-independent-living-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20didn't%20think%20I%20was%20the%20type%20of%20person%20who%20would%20enjoy%20living%20in%20a%20retirement%20community.%20My%20new%20social%20calendar%20says%20otherwise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Maureen%20Rubin)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tata%2C%20JSW%20Group%20to%20invest%20nearly%20%241%20billion%20in%20EV%2C%20battery%20technologies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778145404000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2026-05%2F07%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F1200X628%2F1778145383-8781.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Ftata-jsw-group-to-invest-nearly-1-billion-in-ev-battery-technologies-126050700854_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tata%20Group%20and%20JSW%20Group%20are%20separately%20funding%20research%20and%20development%20centers%20aimed%20at%20building%20in-house%20expertise%20in%20next-generation%20battery%20technologies%20and%20advanced%20EV%20systems%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fauto%2Ftata-jsw-group-to-invest-nearly-1-billion-in-ev-battery-technologies-126050700854_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%