2C%20and%20is%20based%20in%20New%20York.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20my%20startup%20had%20a%20problem%20when%20our%20food%20budget%20hit%20over%20%2413%2C500%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%2C%20most%20of%20that%20money%20was%20spent%20on%20DoorDash.%20Paying%20for%20the%20team's%20meals%20is%20a%20super%20important%20part%20of%20moving%20fast%20for%20us.%20I%20think%20it%20saves%20at%20least%20two%20hours%20a%20day%20because%20no%20one%20has%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuperhuman-boosts-office-attendance-new-incentive-plan-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleave%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20moved%20into%20a%20new%20office%20with%20a%20kitchen%20and%20realized%20that%20having%20a%20private%20chef%20would%20probably%20be%20much%20cheaper%20than%20ordering%20meals%20every%20day.%20Within%20a%20week%20or%20so%2C%20my%20cofounder%20and%20I%20hired%20someone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20might%20seem%20odd%20for%20a%20team%20of%20eight%20to%20have%20a%20professional%20cook%2C%20but%20I%20doubt%20the%20chef%20will%20make%20me%20bankrupt%20or%20give%20the%20company%20a%20negative%20connotation%20that%20will%20ruin%20its%20trajectory.%20Even%20though%20I%20got%20some%20initial%20pushback%2C%20this%20change%20has%20given%20us%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusy-dietitian-daily-diet-protein-fiber-gut-health-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eopportunity%20to%20be%20healthier%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20more%20productive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20wants%20to%20talk%20to%20founders%20of%20AI-powered%20companies%20with%20fewer%20than%2010%20workers%2C%20and%20employees%20working%20alongside%20AI%20agents%20and%20bots%2C%20to%20understand%20what%20the%20%26quot%3BTiny%20Teams%26quot%3B%20era%20really%20feels%20like%20%E2%80%94%20the%20wins%2C%20the%20fears%2C%20and%20the%20human%20skills%20that%20stand%20out.%20Share%20your%20story%20by%20filling%20out%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScO-Lptuw9eirYFmkAfOKc1aOvrFIW1jT2FzxuLJSexsTLExg%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dheader%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equick%20form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c0f317cd-1c4f-4dc5-afc2-45c620fd6a6f%5C%22%3ESome%20employees%20told%20me%20I%20was%20a%20little%20crazy%20for%20suggesting%20hiring%20a%20private%20chef%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20team%20loved%20being%20able%20to%20order%20what%20they%20wanted%20from%20DoorDash.%20So%2C%20I%20knew%20the%20chef%20had%20to%20be%20good%20enough%20to%20beat%20the%20appeal%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-mac-mcdonalds-uber-eats-price-experiment-delivery-fee-charges-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eordering%20from%20any%20restaurant%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20posted%20on%20TikTok%20looking%20for%20a%20chef%2C%20then%20reached%20out%20to%20people%20who%20showed%20interest%20in%20the%20comments%20and%20started%20interviewing.%20The%20first%20interview%20and%20test%20meal%20didn't%20go%20well%2C%20but%20I%20still%20wanted%20to%20pursue%20the%20idea%20a%20bit%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20interviewed%20and%20had%20test%20meals%20with%20a%20few%20candidates.%20The%20chef%20we%20hired%20was%20the%20third%20person%20we%20tested.%20Her%20food%20was%20amazing%2C%20and%20by%20then%20the%20team%20was%20convinced%20that%20a%20chef%20would%20be%20a%20good%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2231ba86c2-2126-4515-89b7-02ad710a3ee3%5C%22%3EOur%20company%20chef%20works%20more%20typical%20hours%20than%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20team%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20chef%20works%20more%20typical%209-to-5%20hours.%20This%20can%20vary%20based%20on%20our%20operational%20needs.%20Her%20salary%20is%20lower%20than%20that%20of%20employees%20on%20the%20business%20side%2C%20but%20she%20makes%20in%20the%20high%205-figure%20range.%20In%20addition%20to%20her%20salary%2C%20she%20also%20gets%20a%20free%20gym%20membership%20and%20a%20grocery%20stipend%20to%20use%20for%20the%20team's%20meals%20each%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20nine%20of%20us%20total%2C%20including%20her.%20She%20prepares%20three%20family-style%20meals%20for%20us%20throughout%20the%20day.%20Some%20people%20have%20dietary%20restrictions%20and%20caloric%20goals%2C%20so%20she%20accounts%20for%20that%2C%20and%20we%20weigh%20in%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-splurging-on-free-lunch-perks-catering-microsoft-meta-google-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20weekly%20menu%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223568%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20smiling%20woman%20serves%20plated%20dishes%20to%20three%20seated%20men%20gathered%20around%20a%20large%20wooden%20table%20in%20a%20bright%20dining%20room.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb4e4c5edd94d1e7339bc6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222676%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESeries%20private%20chef%20at%20their%20office%20in%20New%20York%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Nathaneo%20Johnson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20tries%20to%20make%20healthy%20meals%20for%20us.%20Breakfast%20is%20usually%20something%20like%20maple%20bacon%2C%20protein%20pancakes%2C%20and%20green%20juice.%20Lunch%20will%20be%20chicken%20meatballs%20or%20buffalo%20hot%20honey%20cornflake%20chicken%20tenders%20with%20a%20salad%2C%20and%20we%20also%20request%20steak%20a%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEveryone%20has%20been%20happy%20with%20it%20for%20the%20most%20part.%20There%20are%20a%20few%20people%20who%20are%20nitpicky%20and%20complain%2C%20but%20people%20can%20still%20order%20food%20with%20their%20own%20money%20if%20they'd%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ad81c50e-9f22-42f3-86e8-7e56c287cb91%5C%22%3EEating%20healthier%20has%20increased%20our%20productivity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20benefit%2C%20honestly%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsnacks-nutrition-scientist-eats-boost-heart-health-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20nutrients%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20balance%20of%20the%20meals%20we%20eat%20now.%20When%20we%20were%20ordering%20food%20constantly%2C%20we%20didn't%20eat%20as%20healthily.%20Especially%20when%20it%20got%20late%2C%20and%20we%20would%20order%20from%20places%20like%20Five%20Guys%20or%20Popeyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20realized%20that%20little%20things%20like%20having%20green%20juice%20in%20the%20morning%20every%20day%20can%20help%20me%20start%20my%20day%20the%20right%20way%20more%20than%20anything%20else.%20I%20don't%20feel%20as%20much%20brain%20fog%20anymore.%20I%20feel%20more%20productive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20think%20the%20benefits%20will%20compound%20over%20time%2C%20with%20people%20hopefully%20getting%20sick%20less%20and%20overall%20taking%20better%20care%20of%20their%20diets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223202%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20overhead%20view%20shows%20a%20woman%20arranging%20several%20plated%20dishes%2C%20including%20grilled%20salmon%2C%20skewers%2C%20and%20salad%2C%20on%20a%20wooden%20table.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb4ed7e3f2a46ca8fcf81d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222401%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20team%20weighs%20in%20on%20a%20weekly%20menu.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Nathaneo%20Johnson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bbeb6768-b9db-4f34-9063-c60d560e7661%5C%22%3EI%20wouldn't%20recommend%20this%20for%20every%20startup%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20a%20company%20needs%20the%20right%20setup%20in%20its%20office%20for%20a%20private%20chef%20to%20work.%20We're%20blessed%20to%20have%20this%20mixed%20space%20in%20New%20York%20with%20a%20separate%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20aren't%20seeing%2C%20smelling%2C%20or%20hearing%20anything%20happening%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20Our%20chef%20just%20tells%20us%20to%20come%20to%20the%20conference%20room%20when%20the%20food%20is%20in%20there.%20I%20don't%20think%20having%20a%20chef%20would%20work%20for%20us%20without%20this%20setup.%20Things%20would%20probably%20get%20crowded%2C%20and%20I%20wouldn't%20want%20to%20be%20smelling%20food%20all%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a28af0ac-93aa-4bf6-8524-e4431b56b144%5C%22%3EAs%20soon%20as%20an%20AI%20model%20can%20cook%20for%20us%2C%20we'll%20try%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20recently%20reduced%20the%20team%20by%20a%20few%20people%20to%20ensure%20each%20role%20was%20really%20necessary.%20We%20had%20a%20chief%20of%20staff%20at%20one%20point.%20That%20was%20one%20role%20we%20experimented%20with%2C%20but%20it%20didn't%20seem%20like%20a%20great%20fit%20given%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-execs-on-pros-cons-managing-tiny-teams-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehow%20small%20the%20team%20is%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20not%20a%20specialist%2C%20if%20you%20can't%20do%20anything%20that's%20better%20than%20everyone%20else%20in%20the%20room%2C%20then%20you%20shouldn't%20be%20here.%20I%20think%20creativity%20and%20vision%20will%20always%20be%20shaped%20by%20humans.%20Everything%20else%20can%20and%20probably%20will%20be%20replaced%2C%20to%20an%20extent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%2C%20hiring%20a%20personal%20chef%2C%20was%20about%20efficiency%20and%20costs%2C%20but%20I%20definitely%20think%20a%20chef%20can%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-engineers-lessons-white-collar-works-ai-disruption-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereplaced%20by%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20near%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20Tiny%20Teams%20story%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%2C%20Agnes%20Applegate%2C%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aaapplegate%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eaapplegate%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiny-ai-startup-hired-private-chef-costs-productivity-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778145061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb502ef9e4752b6d601585%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiny-ai-startup-hired-private-chef-costs-productivity-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20startup%20CEO%20hired%20a%20private%20chef%20for%20his%208-person%20team%20after%20spending%20%2413%2C500%20monthly%20on%20food%20delivery.%20It%20saved%20money%20and%20boosted%20productivity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aapplegate%40insider.com%20(Agnes%20Applegate)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20UX%20design%20job%20allowed%20me%20to%20pivot%20into%20a%20role%20where%20I%20explain%20AI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221877%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sajani%20Lokuge%20%20sitting%20with%20mic%20in%20front%20of%20her%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f8bb3c9a23d20d291b605f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221408%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESajani%20Lokuge%20said%20she%20leverages%20her%20technical%20background%20in%20her%20new%20role.%3Cp%3ESajani%20Lokuge%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESajani%20Lokuge%20pivoted%20from%20UX%20design%20to%20AI%20communications%20after%20growing%20her%20LinkedIn%20following.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%2026-year-old%20now%20uses%20her%20UX%20skillset%20in%20AI%20content%20strategy%2C%20hosting%20podcasts%20and%20town%20halls.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHer%20job%20involves%20translating%20technical%20AI%20concepts%20for%20a%20general%20audience.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Sajani%20Lokuge%2C%20a%2026-year-old%20AI%20content%20manager%20at%20an%20industrial%20AI%20software%20company.%20She%20is%20based%20in%20Colombo%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%3C%2Fem%3E.%3Cem%3E%20Her%20identity%20and%20employment%20have%20been%20verified%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20studied%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-engineers-lessons-white-collar-works-ai-disruption-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esoftware%20engineering%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20started%20my%20career%20as%20a%20UX%20designer.%20I%20worked%20my%20way%20up%20to%20lead%20UX%20designer.%20I%20used%20to%20work%20in%20a%20very%20technical%20role%20involved%20in%20making%20the%20product%20%E2%80%94%20and%20now%20my%20job%20is%20mostly%20about%20broadcasting%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoughly%2010%20months%20ago%2C%20I%20transitioned%20to%20an%20AI%20content%20manager%20at%20my%20company%2C%20where%20I%20head%20the%20AI%20communication%20and%20content%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20part%20of%20an%20ongoing%20series%20about%20workers%20who%20transitioned%20into%20AI%20roles.%20Did%20you%20pivot%20to%20AI%3F%20We%20want%20to%20hear%20from%20you.%20Reach%20out%20to%20the%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aaaltchek%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3Eaaltchek%40insider.com%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20secure-messaging%20platform%20Signal%20at%20%3Cstrong%3Eaalt.19%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20switch%20happened%20because%20my%20company%20needed%20someone%20who%20could%20explain%20what%20we%20were%20building%20to%20internal%20and%20external%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20already%20spent%20years%20inside%20the%20company%20doing%20design%20work%20and%20translating%20technical%20problems%20to%20users.%20I%20was%20also%20building%20a%20public%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-engineer-said-landing-ai-role-took-year-daily-upskilling-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplatform%20on%20LinkedIn%20around%20design%20careers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20AI%2C%20which%20now%20has%20about%2026%2C000%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20career%20has%20always%20been%20about%20making%20complex%20systems%20understandable%20to%20people%20who%20have%20to%20use%20them%2C%20and%20this%20was%20the%20next%20logical%20step%20in%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I%20develop%20AI%20adoption%20messaging.%20I%20produce%20and%20moderate%20our%20AI%20global%20town%20hall%2C%20which%20is%20a%20monthly%20executive%20broadcast%20that%20goes%20out%20to%20all%20our%20employees%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20produce%20and%20host%20a%20video%20podcast%20series%20called%20%26quot%3BVoices%20of%20Industry%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20I%20sit%20down%20with%20senior%20leaders%20across%20domains%2C%20and%20talk%20about%20how%20they're%20adopting%20industrial%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20weeks%2C%20I%20lean%20into%20the%20video%20production%20part%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20lot%20of%20traveling.%20Some%20weeks%2C%20I%20do%20more%20strategic%20communication.%20Others%20I%20do%20more%20sales%20enablement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cffb70be-0829-4399-ae00-c1e5f2b9decc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20skills%20were%20transferable%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20job%20of%20a%20UX%20designer%20is%20to%20figure%20out%20what%20someone%20is%20trying%20to%20do%20and%20why%20they're%20getting%20stuck.%20That%20skill%20transfers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-manager-explains-how-she-pivoted-from-admin-to-ai-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edirectly%20to%20AI%20communication%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20if%20I'm%20planning%20a%20town%20hall%20or%20producing%20a%20podcast%20episode%2C%20I%20have%20to%20do%20research%20first%20and%20figure%20out%20who's%20going%20to%20watch%2C%20what%20they%20know%2C%20and%20what%20questions%20they're%20going%20to%20walk%20away%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmpathy%20is%20another%20transferable%20skill%20that%20is%20very%20important%20for%20any%20UX%20designer.%20Designers%20watch%20users%20struggle%20and%20learn%20to%20make%20decisions%20that%20are%20best%20for%20the%20person.%20That's%20most%20of%20the%20job%20when%20I'm%20explaining%20AI%20to%20people%20who%20don't%20speak%20the%20technical%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20job%20titles%20are%20shifting%2C%20but%20the%20underlying%20work%20and%20skills%20of%20a%20UX%20designer%20aren't%20going%20anywhere.%20Instead%20of%20designing%20screens%20and%20interfaces%2C%20I'm%20designing%20how%20people%20understand%20a%20new%20category%20of%20products.%20The%20principles%20are%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dc4f80ca-68be-42d6-a330-f964fe116dea%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20learned%20on%20the%20job%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPosting%20about%20AI%20got%20me%20visibility%2C%20but%20I%20still%20had%20to%20build%20my%20technical%20fluency.%20It%20wasn't%20about%20learning%20how%20to%20code%2C%20but%20understanding%20our%20AI%20products%20so%20that%20I%20could%20interview%20industrial%20leaders%20and%20translate%20what%20we%20were%20building%20into%20something%20that%20a%20non-technical%20audience%20could%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20three%20months%20in%20my%20new%20role%2C%20I%20embedded%20myself%20into%20AI%20product%20teams.%20I%20sat%20in%20their%20stand-ups%20and%20I%20asked%20questions%20that%20probably%20sounded%20dumb%20%E2%80%94%20until%20they%20weren't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20my%20upskilling%20was%20structured%20around%20the%20work%20itself.%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20wait%20to%20learn%2C%20and%20then%20do%20the%20work.%20In%20my%20experience%20though%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoftware-engineer-landed-job-in-ai-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ework%20and%20the%20learning%3C%2Fa%3E%20happened%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e1d66399-53f5-46be-b1b7-f67b019da11a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20wait%20to%20feel%20ready%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20very%20comfortable%20and%20happy%20in%20my%20previous%20role%20as%20the%20lead%20UX%20designer.%20I%20wasn't%20looking%20to%20leave%2C%20but%20when%20this%20opportunity%20came%20up%2C%20I%20couldn't%20say%20no.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20advice%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-workers-explain-how-they-added-ai-job-title-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epeople%20who%20want%20to%20make%20a%20similar%20pivot%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%3A%20Stop%20waiting%20to%20feel%20ready.%20The%20people%20inside%20AI%20organizations%20are%20figuring%20it%20out%20in%20real%20time%2C%20too.%20If%20you're%20a%20designer%2C%20you%20already%20have%20most%20of%20what%20this%20role%20requires.%20The%20AI%20part%20is%20learnable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20get%20an%20AI%20certificate%20and%20hope%20someone%20hires%20you.%20You%20have%20to%20produce%20work%20that%20proves%20you%20can%20explain%20AI%20to%20an%20audience.%20That's%20how%20I%20got%20noticed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20role%20even%20existed%2C%20I'd%20been%20publicly%20posting%20about%20design%20careers%20and%20AI%20for%20months.%20By%20the%20time%20the%20role%20was%20being%20created%2C%20the%20leadership%20team%20already%20had%20a%20sense%20of%20how%20I%20thought%2C%20what%20kind%20of%20work%20I%20produced%2C%20and%20what%20my%20strengths%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20advice%20for%20designers%20specifically%20is%20not%20to%20treat%20your%20portfolio%20as%20this%20static%20folder%20of%20past%20projects%2C%20but%20more%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fresume-helped-pivot-from-software-engineering-to-ai-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliving%20body%20of%20public%3C%2Fa%3E%20work.%20Write%20publicly.%20Show%20people%20like%20how%20you%20think%20about%20AI%20before%20they%20even%20interview%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fux-designer-shares-how-she-pivoted-to-ai-communications-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778144881000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69f8bb3c9a23d20d291b605f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fux-designer-shares-how-she-pivoted-to-ai-communications-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sajani%20Lokuge%20says%20she%20built%20a%20LinkedIn%20following%20by%20posting%20about%20AI%20and%20careers%20before%20she%20was%20approached%20for%20the%20role.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aaltchek%40insider.com%20(Ana%20Altchek)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Govt%20likely%20to%20divest%20stake%20worth%20%241.06%20billion%20in%20Coal%20India%20via%20OFS%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778144809000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-08%2F02%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X628%2F1690996539-0715.JPG%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgovt-likely-to-divest-stake-worth-1-06-billion-in-coal-india-via-ofs-126050700719_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20government%20held%20a%2063.13%20per%20cent%20stake%20in%20Coal%20India%20as%20of%20%E2%80%8BMarch%2031%2C%20according%20to%20LSEG%20data%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgovt-likely-to-divest-stake-worth-1-06-billion-in-coal-india-via-ofs-126050700719_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgovt-likely-to-divest-stake-worth-1-06-billion-in-coal-india-via-ofs-126050700719_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgovt-likely-to-divest-stake-worth-1-06-billion-in-coal-india-via-ofs-126050700719_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Actors%20say%20their%20faces%20are%20being%20used%20in%20fake%20AI%20sex%20scenes%20to%20sell%20micro%20dramas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22From%20left%3A%20vertical%20actors%20Tess%20Dinerstein%2C%20David%20Eves%2C%20Faith%20Orta%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fa7e525edd94d1e7339955%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFrom%20left%3A%20vertical%20actors%20Tess%20Dinerstein%2C%20David%20Eves%2C%20and%20Faith%20Orta%3Cp%3EGregory%20Wallace%2C%20Yellowbelly%2C%20Yellowbelly%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EActors%20say%20micro%20drama%20apps%20manipulated%20their%20images%20to%20create%20misleading%2C%20sexual%20promos.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20AI-generated%20ads%20showed%20sexual%20scenes%20that%20didn't%20appear%20in%20the%20actual%20shows.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20actors%20said%20they%20were%20blindsided%20and%20fear%20the%20ads%20could%20hurt%20their%20reputations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20ad%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhollywood-wants-to-capitalize-on-mini-vertical-dramas-reelshort-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emicro%20drama%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BHow%20to%20Tame%20a%20Silver%20Fox%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20age-gap%20romance%2C%20opens%20with%20a%20shot%20of%20a%20woman%2C%20then%20cuts%20to%20two%20people%20having%20sex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20promo%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freelshort-taking-on-hollywood-short-dramas-courts-creators-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EReelShort%20show%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20a%20shock%20to%20Tess%20Dinerstein%2C%20the%20woman%20in%20the%20scene.%20The%20reason%3A%20There%20wasn't%20any%20sex%20or%20nudity%20in%20the%20show%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20really%20jarring%2C%26quot%3B%20Dinerstein%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Dinerstein%20said%20she%20worries%20that%20people%20won't%20take%20her%20seriously%20as%20an%20actor%20if%20they%20see%20the%20promo.%20She%20also%20worries%20about%20how%20her%20parents%20could%20react.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20like%20it%20delegitimized%20the%20work%20I%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20so%20grateful%20to%20be%20an%20actor%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20take%20my%20clothes%20off.%20Nothing%20against%20people%20who%20do%2C%20but%20I%20don't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDinerstein%20has%20become%20a%20prominent%20actor%20in%20the%20world%20of%20micro%20dramas%2C%20also%20called%20verticals%20or%20mini%20dramas.%20These%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffans-describe-the-appeal-of-micro-dramas-escapism-actor-interaction-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esoapy%20series%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20short%20episodes%20%E2%80%94%20often%20one%20to%20two%20minutes%20%E2%80%94%20and%20are%20made%20for%20mobile%20viewing.%20They're%20on%20the%20rise%20in%20the%20US%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deloitte.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Finsights%2Findustry%2Ftechnology%2Ftechnology-media-and-telecom-predictions%2F2026%2Fshort-form-video-series.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeloitte%20predicted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20revenue%20made%20by%20micro%20drama%20apps%20would%20more%20than%20double%20this%20year%20to%20%247.8%20billion%2C%20with%20the%20US%20accounting%20for%20nearly%20half%20of%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20apps%2C%20many%20of%20which%20originated%20in%20Asia%2C%20are%20fighting%20tooth%20and%20nail%20for%20US%20market%20share.%20Industry%20insiders%20say%20the%20marketing%20costs%20to%20attract%20new%20users%20are%20sky-high%2C%20which%20incentivizes%20companies%20to%20make%20promos%20as%20eye-catching%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20app%20may%20boast%20of%20a%20show%20that%20makes%20%2430%20million%2C%20but%20%2427%20million%20of%20it%20will%20have%20gone%20to%20advertising%2C%26quot%3B%20Thom%20Woodley%2C%20a%20longtime%20verticals%20producer%2C%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicro-dramas-face-reality-check-after-buzzy-us-arrival-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20quest%20for%20new%20viewers%2C%20some%20apps%20are%20angering%20their%20actors%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Dinerstein%20%E2%80%94%20by%20creating%20misleading%2C%20sexualized%20promos%20to%20lure%20people%20to%20their%20shows.%20Three%20actors%20said%20when%20they%20complained%20to%20the%20apps%2C%20they%20were%20told%20the%20ads%20were%20made%20by%20third%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223b6c1ee0-85ab-413b-bf0e-370864c4335c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Not%20everyone%20knows%20I%20didn't%20agree%20to%20do%20that'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EActor%20Faith%20Orta%20said%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bflabbergasted%26quot%3B%20to%20see%20an%20ad%20pop%20up%20on%20her%20TikTok%20feed%20that%20showed%20a%20man%20pulling%20off%20her%20top%20and%20grabbing%20her%20breast%2C%20which%20was%20blurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20real%20scene%2C%20he%20never%20even%20grabbed%20my%20breast%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20very%20body%20positive%2C%20and%20I'm%20all%20about%20consent.%20When%20AI%20jumps%20in%20and%20shows%20the%20audience%20something%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20show%2C%20it%20takes%20away%20the%20power%20over%20my%20own%20body.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsora-copyright-images-sam-altman-openai-hollywood-studios-fight-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20has%20made%20it%20easy%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20create%20fake%20videos%20that%20look%20real%2C%20and%20actors%20say%20these%20sexualized%20ads%20can%20have%20emotional%2C%20reputational%2C%20and%20financial%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDavid%20Eves%20said%20he%20was%20caught%20off%20guard%20when%20someone%20sent%20him%20an%20ad%20for%20a%20vertical%20he%20was%20in%2C%20%26quot%3BTurn%20the%20Mafia's%20Virgin%20Wife%20On%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20showed%20his%20likeness%20in%20a%20threesome.%20Eves%20said%20he%20never%20shot%20a%20threesome%20and%20wouldn't%20have%20consented%20to%20such%20a%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNot%20everyone%20knows%20I%20didn't%20agree%20to%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22873%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshot%20from%20%26quot%3BTurn%20the%20Mafia's%20Virgin%20Wife%20On%26quot%3B%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb632b5edd94d1e7339cbf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22655%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDavid%20Eves%20said%20a%20promo%20for%20%26quot%3BTurn%20the%20Mafia's%20Virgin%20Wife%20On%26quot%3B%20put%20his%20likeness%20in%20a%20sex%20scene%20he%20wasn't%20actually%20in.%3Cp%3EAnyreel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EActor%20Haley%20Lohrli%20said%20she%20started%20getting%20creepy%20messages%20from%20fans%20after%20a%20series%20of%20ads%20for%20a%20film%20she%20starred%20in%20circulated.%20The%20ad%20showed%20her%20in%20a%20bra%20and%20underwear%2C%20though%20she%20was%20fully%20clothed%20in%20the%20film.%20When%20she%20contacted%20the%20app%20that%20distributed%20the%20film%2C%20she%20was%20told%20there%20were%20some%20300%20variations%20of%20the%20ad%20out%20there%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20feels%20so%20gross%20to%20see%20videos%20of%20yourself%20that's%20not%20even%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVertical%20actors%20are%20sharing%20their%20stories%20on%20social%20media%20and%20urging%20others%20to%20include%20contract%20clauses%20requiring%20consent%20for%20AI%20manipulation%20of%20their%20image%20or%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELohrli%20said%20she%20now%20insists%20on%20language%20in%20her%20contracts%20that%20protects%20her%20likeness%20from%20AI%20manipulation.%20Lohrli%20said%20she's%20worked%20with%20multiple%20producers%20since%20then%20and%20hasn't%20gotten%20any%20pushback%20on%20the%20contract%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experiences%20of%20these%20micro%20drama%20actors%20are%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20threat%20the%20profession%20faces%20as%20AI%20makes%20synthetic%20videos%20increasingly%20realistic%20and%20cheap%20to%20create.%20Actors%20are%20taking%20steps%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20trademarking%20themselves%20%E2%80%94%20to%20protect%20against%20AI%20video%20generators%20using%20their%20likenesses.%20The%20actors'%20union%20SAG-AFTRA%20struck%20an%20agreement%20with%20the%20major%20Hollywood%20studios%20in%202023%20that%20included%20a%20ban%20on%20the%20use%20of%20digital%20replicas%20without%20consent%2C%20and%20is%20seeking%20stronger%20AI%20protections%20in%20this%20year's%20contract%20negotiations%20with%20the%20studios%20and%20streamers.%20The%20two%20sides%20reached%20a%20tentative%20agreement%20on%20May%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22634%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Promo%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20Fake%20Debutante%20and%20The%20True%20Billionaire%26quot%3B%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb634c5edd94d1e7339cc0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22476%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFaith%20Orta%20said%20her%20image%20was%20manipulated%20for%20a%20promo%20for%20%26quot%3BThe%20Fake%20Debutante%20and%20The%20True%20Billionaire.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EDramaBox%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229d06a2a5-dbdd-43b1-b81d-39ba50d96917%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EActors%20have%20little%20recourse%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEves%20said%20he%20figured%20contacting%20Anyreel%2C%20the%20platform%20where%20the%20ad%20for%20%26quot%3BTurn%20the%20Mafia's%20Virgin%20Wife%20On%26quot%3B%20appeared%2C%20would%20be%20a%20waste%20of%20time.%20He%20plans%20to%20ensure%20his%20next%20contract%20has%20AI%20protections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDinerstein%20said%20she%20reached%20out%20to%20ReelShort's%20CEO%20about%20the%20%26quot%3BHow%20to%20Tame%20a%20Silver%20Fox%26quot%3B%20ad.%20She%20said%20the%20company%20told%20her%20the%20ad%20was%20created%20by%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Beijing%20team%26quot%3B%20and%20then%20took%20it%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnyreel%20and%20ReelShort%20didn't%20respond%20to%20multiple%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJonathan%20Handel%2C%20an%20entertainment%20lawyer%2C%20said%20a%20standard%20actor%20contract%20generally%20gives%20the%20producer%20broad%20rights%20to%20use%20the%20performer's%20image%20and%20voice.%20Overall%2C%20cases%20of%20actors%20successfully%20fighting%20producers%20over%20the%20use%20of%20their%20likeness%20are%20rare%20for%20that%20reason%2C%20he%20said.%20Actors%20can%20seek%20contractual%20restrictions%20that%20prevent%20their%20image%20from%20being%20sexualized%20for%20promotional%20purposes%2C%20though%20that%20might%20prompt%20the%20producer%20to%20hire%20a%20different%20performer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20the%20leverage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20the%20brutal%20reality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EActors'%20contracts%20are%20often%20signed%20with%20a%20show's%20producer%2C%20who%20then%20sells%20the%20film%20to%20an%20app.%20It's%20the%20app%20that%20promotes%20the%20vertical%20on%20social%20media.%20And%20micro%20drama%20actors%20are%20largely%20early-career%20and%20nonunion%2C%20making%20it%20potentially%20risky%20to%20speak%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELindsay%20Lieberman%2C%20a%20lawyer%20specializing%20in%20cyber%20sexual%20misconduct%2C%20said%20many%20states%20have%20laws%20addressing%20the%20nonconsensual%20distribution%20of%20intimate%20images%2C%20and%20a%20growing%20number%20are%20expanding%20those%20laws%20to%20cover%20AI-generated%20or%20digitally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flawsuit-allegation-xai-grok-created-sexualized-deepfakes-minors-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ealtered%20sexual%20content%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Whether%20those%20laws%20apply%20in%20a%20given%20case%20would%20depend%20on%20the%20scope%20of%20consent%20in%20any%20underlying%20contract.%20She%20said%20pursuing%20overseas%20companies%20is%20often%20impractical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226f552e53-3bb9-458c-9564-0a888f4336c8%5C%22%3ETech%20companies%20play%20a%20part%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-launches-a-new-micro-drama-app-called-pinedrama-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eand%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20play%20a%20role.%20Apps%20use%20the%20platforms%20to%20promote%20and%20distribute%20their%20titles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20and%20TikTok%20prohibit%20sexual%20activity%20or%20nudity%20in%20ads%20and%20organic%20content%20and%20have%20policies%20requiring%20labels%20for%20AI-generated%20content.%20Some%20content%20slips%20past%20those%20controls%2C%20reports%20have%20found.%20A%202026%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2Fai-artificial-intelligence%2F900400%2Ftiktok-ai-ads-labels-samsung-disclosure%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Verge%3C%2Fa%3E%20identified%20AI%20ads%20that%20appeared%20on%20TikTok%20without%20disclosures%2C%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faiforensics.org%2Fwork%2Fmeta-porn-ads%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2025%20research%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20Meta-owned%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%20distributed%20thousands%20of%20porn%20images%2C%20including%20AI-generated%20ones.%20A%20Meta%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%20removed%20the%20violating%20content%20that%20was%20shared%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-deal-finalized-what-changes-ownership-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETikTok%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20it's%20helped%20label%201.3%20billion%20videos%20and%20has%20created%20resources%20to%20educate%20people%20on%20spotting%20deepfakes.%20A%20Meta%20rep%20said%20the%20company%20is%20continuously%20working%20to%20improve%20its%20AI%20labeling%2C%20and%20added%20that%20identifying%20such%20content%20can%20be%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDinerstein%20said%20she%20worries%20about%20how%20the%20AI%20technology%20will%20be%20used%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%2C%20she%20saw%20an%20ad%20for%20a%20new%20project%20of%20hers%2C%20%26quot%3BHigh%20School%20Diary%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20had%20her%20saying%20something%20about%20being%20a%20virgin%20that%20she%20didn't%20say%20in%20the%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%20obviously%20not%20as%20scary%20as%20having%20deepfake%20porn%20made%2C%20but%20it's%20sexual%20in%20nature%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20can%20make%20me%20say%20that%2C%20they%20can%20make%20me%20say%20anything.%20And%20if%20I%20don't%20throw%20a%20fit%20over%20this%2C%20who%20knows%20how%20far%20they'll%20take%20it%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Factors-sexualized-fake-ads-promote-micro-dramas-tiktok-meta-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778144702000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fa7e525edd94d1e7339955%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Factors-sexualized-fake-ads-promote-micro-dramas-tiktok-meta-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Actors%20say%20micro%20drama%20apps%20manipulated%20their%20images%20in%20misleading%20ads.%20They%20say%20the%20ads%20can%20cause%20emotional%20and%20career%20damage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lmoses%40insider.com%20(Lucia%20Moses)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20an%20executive%20coach.%20Here%20are%205%20ways%20I'm%20telling%20my%20clients%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20get%20ahead%20at%20work.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22headshot%20of%20a%20woman%20in%20yellow%20with%20a%20black%20background%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fa2e7e38bee05c96984083%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndrea%20Wasserman.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Andrea%20Wasserman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECareer%20coach%20Andrea%20Wasserman%20advises%20leaders%20to%20use%20AI%20to%20improve%20their%20competitive%20edge%20at%20work.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20suggests%20enhancing%20your%20communication%20by%20simplifying%20complex%20ideas%20for%20varied%20audiences%20with%20an%20AI%20tool.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EProfessionals%20can%20also%20better%20articulate%20their%20achievements%2C%20enhancing%20visibility%20in%20career%20settings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frelationships-prioritize-work-want-promotion-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecareer%20coach%3C%2Fa%3E%20working%20with%20directors%20through%20C-level%20leaders%20in%20retail%2C%20tech%2C%20finance%2C%20real%20estate%2C%20and%20other%20industries.%20When%20my%20clients%20ask%20me%20how%20they%20should%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-that-monitor-workers-can-use-data-train-ai-agents-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Euse%20AI%20at%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20their%20real%20question%20is%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20I%20stay%20competitive%20as%20expectations%20change%20and%20my%20colleagues%20leverage%20new%20tools%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20use%20AI%20to%20get%20through%20their%20to-do%20lists%20faster%2C%20while%20others%20use%20it%20to%20enhance%20their%20thinking%2C%20fine-tune%20how%20they%20communicate%2C%20and%20make%20their%20value%20easier%20to%20recognize.%20The%20tool%20may%20be%20the%20same%2C%20but%20the%20outcomes%20can%20be%20very%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20ways%20you%20can%20use%20AI%20to%20accelerate%20your%20career%20in%20practice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fa8a3d93-c933-403f-a60f-3af4cd9734b1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Pressure-test%20your%20thinking%20before%20you%20share%20it%20with%20anyone%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EToo%20many%20people%20walk%20into%20meetings%20while%20they're%20still%20forming%20their%20point%20of%20view%20or%20thinking%20about%20how%20they'll%20respond%20to%20questions.%20As%20they%20talk%2C%20you%20can%20hear%20that%20the%20idea%20is%20there%2C%20but%20it%20isn't%20fully%20developed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20maintain%20and%20build%20their%20credibility%2C%20I%20have%20clients%20use%20an%20AI%20tool%20before%20they%20begin%20circulating%20their%20ideas%20out%20loud.%20I%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-read-my-boyfriends-chatgpt-broke-up-dont-regret-it-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20it's%20worth%20trying%20Claude%20and%20Perplexity%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20about%20being%20fed%20the%20answers%2C%20but%20about%20challenging%20yourself%20to%20be%20better%20prepared.%20Input%20your%20idea%20into%20an%20AI%20tool%20and%20ask%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWhere%20are%20the%20weak%20spots%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhat%20assumptions%20need%20more%20evidence%20to%20support%20them%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHow%20would%20skeptical%20executives%20who%20represent%20different%20areas%20of%20the%20organization%20respond%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20my%20clients%20who%20do%20this%20are%20in%20the%20rooms%20that%20matter%2C%20they're%20not%20trying%20to%20answer%20these%20questions%20in%20real%20time%20because%20they've%20already%20worked%20through%20obvious%20points%20of%20potential%20pushback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a95f952c-3f0d-4135-9e4f-7f9ba130ada9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Use%20AI%20to%20simplify%20your%20message%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20best%20operators%20I%20see%20often%20struggle%20here.%20They%20know%20their%20subject%20matter%20so%20well%20that%20when%20they%20communicate%20it%20to%20relative%20novices%2C%20they%20make%20the%20message%20too%20dense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20useful%20for%20helping%20craft%20translations%20for%20different%20audiences.%20For%20example%2C%20I'll%20suggest%20clients%20take%20something%20complex%20%E2%80%94%20a%20process%20flow%2C%20a%20strategic%20recommendation%2C%20a%20dataset%20%E2%80%94%20and%20ask%20for%20different%20versions%20of%20it.%20%3Cem%3EHow%20would%20you%20explain%20this%20to%20a%20CFO%3F%20To%20a%20sales%20rep%3F%20To%20a%20board%20member%3F%20To%20someone%20outside%20my%20functional%20area%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20not%20copying%20the%20output.%20They're%20looking%20to%20get%20the%20structure%20and%20level%20of%20detail%20right%20and%20then%20refining%20it%20so%20it%20makes%20sense%20and%20sounds%20like%20them%20%E2%80%94%20just%20clearer%20and%20more%20concise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20the%20tool%20trains%20them%20to%20stop%20over-explaining%20and%20start%20making%20their%20point%20succinctly.%20This%20is%20critical%2C%20as%20brevity%20signals%20confidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22de60a41a-00ff-468a-8298-7a5bb92b44c6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Improve%20how%20you%20talk%20about%20your%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20among%20strong%20performers%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20mistakes%20I%20see%20people%20make%20is%20assuming%20their%20results%20are%20obvious.%20Too%20often%2C%20they're%20not%20%E2%80%94%20either%20because%20others%20aren't%20paying%20attention%2C%20the%20details%20are%20confusing%2C%20or%20the%20impact%20isn't%20understood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20have%20clients%20input%20a%20recent%20project%20or%20decision%20and%20ask%20AI%20to%20draft%20a%20narrative%20that%20spans%20the%20problem(s)%20they%20were%20solving%2C%20the%20trade-offs%20they%20weighed%2C%20and%20what%20changed%20because%20of%20their%20leadership%20or%20involvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20version%20is%20usually%20generic%2C%20but%20it%20gives%20us%20something%20to%20refine%20until%20the%20story%20is%20clear%20and%20appropriately%20impressive%20(not%20exaggerated).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20this%20becomes%20language%20they%20can%20use%20in%20performance%20conversations%2C%20leadership%20updates%2C%20and%20business%20reviews.%20They%20can%20even%20use%20it%20to%20draft%20initial%20public-facing%20content%20for%20platforms%20like%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2201d9c8f5-8a82-4b3a-8aa1-b573b71d0219%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Show%20your%20thinking%20without%20creating%20extra%20work%20for%20yourself%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20know%20they%20should%20be%20sharing%20more%20with%20their%20network%2C%20but%20their%20intent%20to%20be%20proactive%20gets%20buried%20by%20day-to-day%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToo%20often%2C%20being%20strategic%20feels%20optional%20until%20people%20realize%20they're%20being%20overlooked%20for%20opportunities%20that%20require%20it.%20With%20AI%2C%20they%20can%20reduce%20the%20effort%20that's%20required%20to%20share%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20suggest%20clients%20capture%20rough%20thoughts%20as%20they%20come%20to%20mind.%20This%20might%20include%20notes%20after%20a%20meeting%2C%20a%20reaction%20to%20something%20in%20their%20industry%2C%20or%20a%20pattern%20they're%20noticing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20can%20polish%20a%20stream%20of%20consciousness%20or%20aggregate%20several%20streams%20to%20shape%20original%20thoughts%20into%20something%20they%20can%20actually%20share%20in%20person%20with%20a%20manager%20or%20on%20a%20platform%20like%20LinkedIn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20building%20visibility%20in%20regular%20bursts%20rather%20than%20waiting%20until%20they%20have%20all%20the%20time%20they%20would%20like%20to%20sit%20down%20and%20focus%20on%20long-form%20writing%20and%20editing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222f66cdd4-293a-407f-83f2-f8f51ae3ee79%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Reclaim%20your%20time%20and%20apply%20it%20in%20higher-leverage%20ways%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBasic%20uses%20of%20AI%20can%20still%20make%20a%20difference%2C%20such%20as%20writing%20first%20drafts%2C%20summarizing%20inputs%2C%20and%20organizing%20unstructured%20information.%20This%20creates%20time%20savings%2C%20but%20what's%20more%20important%20is%20what%20you%20do%20with%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20see%20clients%20spending%20too%20much%20energy%20on%20execution%20and%20not%20enough%20on%20the%20work%20that%20actually%20drives%20their%20career%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetworking-dos-and-donts-tips-advice-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebuilding%20relationships%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20influencing%20decisions%2C%20gaining%20visibility%20%E2%80%94%20I%20suggest%20they%20use%20AI%20to%20rebalance%20that.%20Having%20AI%20compare%20their%20calendar%20and%20inbox%20against%20their%20goals%20can%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20clients%20gaining%20career%20traction%20from%20AI%20aren't%20only%20using%20it%20to%20produce%20more%20output%3B%20they're%20using%20it%20earlier%20in%20the%20process.%20Before%20a%20meeting%2C%20they've%20already%20worked%20through%20the%20weak%20spots%20in%20their%20thinking.%20Before%20sharing%20an%20idea%2C%20they've%20already%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20explain%20it%20clearly%20to%20their%20audience.%20As%20they%20head%20into%20a%20performance%20conversation%2C%20they've%20already%20developed%20language%20that%20shows%20the%20impact%20of%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey've%20already%20thought%20it%20through%2C%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20explain%20it%2C%20and%20decided%20how%20to%20position%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-use-ai-get-ahead-work-from-executive-coach-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778144701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fa2e7e38bee05c96984083%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-use-ai-get-ahead-work-from-executive-coach-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Career%20coach%20Andrea%20Wasserman%20advises%20her%20clients%20to%20use%20AI%20tools%20to%20enhance%20their%20communication%2C%20simplify%20messages%2C%20and%20reclaim%20their%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Andrea%20Wasserman)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Wadhwa%20Group%20partners%20with%20Arisinfra%20Solutions%20for%20%E2%82%B9650%20cr%20project%20in%20MMR%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778144654000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2025-12%2F25%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F1200X628%2F1766674573-6139.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fwadhwa-group-partners-with-arisinfra-solutions-for-650-cr-project-in-mmr-126050700834_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wadhwa%20Group%20has%20partnered%20with%20ArisUnitern%20RE%20Solutions%20for%20its%20Wadhwa%20Wise%20City%20township%20in%20Panvel%20to%20monetise%20inventory%20worth%20%E2%82%B9650%20crore%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fwadhwa-group-partners-with-arisinfra-solutions-for-650-cr-project-in-mmr-126050700834_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fwadhwa-group-partners-with-arisinfra-solutions-for-650-cr-project-in-mmr-126050700834_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fwadhwa-group-partners-with-arisinfra-solutions-for-650-cr-project-in-mmr-126050700834_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Target%20built%20a%20trend-spotting%20tool%20that's%20speeding%20up%20the%20time%20it%20takes%20to%20get%20new%20fashions%20to%20store%20shelves%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20display%20of%20Target%20apparel%20with%20a%20Western%20theme.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb9fbbe1443b8dc48e2858%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221713%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETarget's%20Western-themed%20collection%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20company's%20new%20AI%20trend-spotter.%3Cp%3EDominick%20Reuter%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFast%20fashion%20brands%20are%20pushing%20a%20new%20pace%20for%20traditional%20retailers%20like%20Target.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20company%20has%20developed%20an%20AI%20tool%20to%20spot%20rising%20trends%20and%20make%20better%20design%20choices.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETarget's%20head%20of%20apparel%20explains%20how%20the%20new%20Trend%20Brain%20is%20taking%20weeks%20out%20of%20product%20lead%20times.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFashion%20keeps%20getting%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetailers%20like%20Temu%20and%20Shein%20are%20setting%20a%20new%20pace%20for%20traditional%20stores%2C%20and%20Target%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-ai-powered-turnaround-plan-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eartifical%20intelligence%20is%20helping%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20meet%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20spring%2C%20the%20bullseye%20retailer%20unveiled%20a%20new%20Trend%20Brain%20tool%20that%20it%20is%20rolling%20out%20to%20designers%20for%20its%20portfolio%20of%20owned-brands%20like%20Wild%20Fable%20and%20Universal%20Thread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tool%20takes%20a%C2%A0predictive%20approach%2C%20drawing%20on%20sources%20ranging%20from%20social%20media%20feeds%20to%20fashion%20show%20catwalk%20photos%20to%20real-time%20purchasing%20trends%2C%20to%20help%20the%20company%20anticipate%20where%20trends%20are%20headed%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20several%20years%20of%20lackluster%20sales%20performance%2C%20Target%20is%20betting%20on%20AI%20to%20speed%20up%20its%20business%2C%20including%20a%20bid%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-bets-on-busy-families-to-return-growth-ceo-fiddelke-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereclaim%20its%20reputation%20for%20style%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETarget's%20head%20of%20apparel%2C%20Gena%20Fox%2C%20explained%20how%20it%20went%20down%20ahead%20of%20the%20all-important%20summer%20swim%20season%20%E2%80%94%20a%20category%20where%20Target%20wants%20to%20maintain%20its%20strong%20share%20of%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20implemented%20this%20digital-first%20model%20to%20read%20silhouettes%2C%20to%20read%20print%20patterns%20and%20other%20trends%20as%20it%20relates%20to%20the%20swim%20business%20more%20broadly%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20at%20a%20meeting%20in%20March.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20then%20able%20to%20get%20those%20online%20very%20quickly%20to%20be%20shipped%20to%20guests.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFox%20said%20the%20tech%20also%20helped%20make%20more%20efficient%20purchasing%20decisions%2C%20such%20as%20when%20it%20flagged%20a%20polka%20dot%20design%20as%20an%20early%20winner%20before%20spring%20even%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20actually%20able%20to%20go%20back%20and%20buy%20into%20more%20and%20then%20move%20out%20of%20styles%20that%20weren't%20performing%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20combination%20of%20AI-assisted%20design%2C%20small-scale%20manufacturing%2C%20and%20shipping%20directly%20to%20customers%20has%20compressed%20what%20is%20historically%20a%20monthslong%20product%20development%20cycle%20into%20a%20matter%20of%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%2C%20the%20strongest%20ideas%20out%20of%20this%20hyper-speed%20process%20are%20given%20the%20full%20retail%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETarget%20said%20the%20Trend%20Brain%20tool%20is%20not%20yet%20rolled%20out%20across%20all%20design%20teams%2C%20and%20the%20company%20still%20relies%20on%20a%20traditional%20product%20development%20strategy%20for%20most%20categories%2C%20but%20it's%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20embrace%20of%20AI%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-retail-ceos-leading-walmart-target-more-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECEO%20Michael%20Fiddelke%3C%2Fa%3E%20aims%20to%20get%20back%20to%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20Trend%20Brain%20not%20only%20works%20faster%20than%20a%20human%20can%2C%20but%20it%20also%20doesn't%20get%20tired.%20That%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20gives%20teams%20time%20back%20to%20focus%20on%20new%20and%20inspiring%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFox%20also%20said%20the%20merchandise%20designers%20aren't%20simply%20sitting%20behind%20a%20computer%20screen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-tried-target-new-app-features-that-make-shopping-easier-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efollowing%20instructions%20from%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20A%20recent%20Western-themed%20collection%20involved%20getting%20a%20little%20dust%20on%20their%20boots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20the%20team%20then%20does%20is%20really%20immerse%20themselves%20in%20the%20trend%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BOur%20team%20went%20to%20rodeos%2C%20they%20went%20to%20mountain%20towns.%20They%20really%20focused%20in%20on%20understanding%20how%20to%20bring%20this%20trend%20to%20life%20in%20a%20way%20that%20no%20one%20else%20can.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-built-ai-trend-brain-predict-what-shoppers-want-next-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778144521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fba01be1443b8dc48e285e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-built-ai-trend-brain-predict-what-shoppers-want-next-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20fashion%20gets%20faster%2C%20Target%20is%20working%20to%20maintain%20its%20leading%20position%20with%20a%20new%20AI%20tool%20that%20spots%20trends%20on%20catwalks%20and%20social%20feeds.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dreuter%40businessinsider.com%20(Dominick%20Reuter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22They%20were%20told%20their%20private%20student%20loans%20were%20paid%20off.%20Then%20they%20were%20sued.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20collage%20featuring%20Ashley%20Carlson%2C%20Hannah%20Bates%2C%20and%20Student%20Loan%20Document.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb700d5edd94d1e7339d1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHannah%20Latham%2C%20Nic%20Antaya%20for%20BI%3B%20Alyssa%20Powell%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20story%20in%20Business%20Insider's%20new%20series%2C%20%26quot%3BStudent%20debt%20spiral%2C%26quot%3B%20examining%20the%20companies%2C%20policies%2C%20and%20financial%20pressures%20reshaping%20how%20Americans%20navigate%20college%20loans.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202024%2C%20Ashley%20Carlson%20got%20an%20unexpected%20email%3A%20%26quot%3BCongrats!%20Your%20SoFi%20Student%20Loan%20is%20100%25%20paid%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2035-year-old%20mom%20of%20two%20couldn't%20believe%20it.%20She%20had%20about%20%2455%2C000%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-student-loan-debt-repayment-struggle-warning-for-federal-borrowers-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunpaid%20student%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20she'd%20borrowed%20to%20finance%20her%20bachelor's%20degree%20in%20construction%20management.%20She%20logged%20into%20her%20account.%20Balance%3A%20%240.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20I%20got%20lucky%20for%20once%2C%26quot%3B%20Carlson%20thought.%20When%20business%20at%20her%20architecture%20firm%20slowed%20in%202023%2C%20she'd%20stopped%20making%20her%20%24800%20monthly%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epayments%20in%20full.%20For%20months%2C%20she'd%20been%20calling%20SoFi%2C%20the%20private%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-grad-plus-new-private-lending-option-repayment-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecompany%20that%20managed%20her%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20asking%20for%20lower%20payments%20or%20a%20financial%20hardship%20forbearance%2C%20without%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarlson%20took%20the%20email%20at%20face%20value%2C%20thinking%20her%20lender%20had%20granted%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-not-happening-borrowers-prepare-debt-repayment-treasury-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erequest%20for%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20didn't%20question%20it%20further.%20She%20wishes%20she%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETen%20months%20after%20the%20%26quot%3BCongrats!%26quot%3B%20email%2C%20a%20manila%20envelope%20appeared%20on%20her%20front%20porch.%20SoFi%20was%20suing%20to%20collect%20her%20full%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20turns%20out%20Carlson's%20loan%20%3Cem%3Ehad%3C%2Fem%3E%20effectively%20disappeared%20in%20February%20%E2%80%94%20not%20because%20it%20was%20forgiven%2C%20but%20because%20it%20was%20transferred%20to%20a%20third%20party.%20To%20this%20day%2C%20she%20doesn't%20know%20where%20her%20balance%20went.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20tabindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20data-media-container%3D%5C%22image%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22img%5C%22%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-figure-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cimg%20data-content-type%3D%5C%22image%2Fjpeg%5C%22%20data-srcs%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Bhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fa295338bee05c9698404b%26quot%3B%3A%7B%26quot%3BcontentType%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bimage%2Fjpeg%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3BaspectRatioW%26quot%3B%3A4160%2C%26quot%3BaspectRatioH%26quot%3B%3A5200%7D%7D%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fa295338bee05c9698404b%3Fwidth%3D1300%26format%3Djpeg%26auto%3Dwebp%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ashley%20Carlson%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%5Cn%3Cfigcaption%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-caption%5C%22%3E%5CnAshley%20Carlson%20is%20representing%20herself%20after%20being%20sued%20by%20her%20private%20student-loan%20lender%2C%20SoFi.%C2%A0%5Cn%3Cspan%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-source%5C%22%3E%5CnHannah%20Latham%20for%20BI%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20an%20extreme%20example%20of%20the%20kind%20of%20confusion%20private%20student-loan%20borrowers%20face%20when%20their%20loans%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-debt-moving-to-treasury-obama-pilot-defaulted-borrowers-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emove%20toward%20default%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20typically%20occurs%20after%20about%20120%20days%20without%20a%20full%20payment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInterviews%20with%20dozens%20of%20borrowers%2C%20lawyers%2C%20and%20industry%20representatives%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20a%20review%20of%20court%20filings%20and%20other%20public%20records%20%E2%80%94%20reveal%20widespread%20confusion%20over%20loan%20balances%20and%20missing%20or%20conflicting%20notices%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-default-social-security-tax-refunds-trump-pause-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eas%20borrowers%20default%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sometimes%20face%20litigation.%20In%20a%20review%20of%20complaints%20about%20private%20lenders%20submitted%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feliminate-cfpb-trump-elon-musk-overdraft-fees-medical-bills-bessent-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EConsumer%20Financial%20Protection%20Bureau%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20Business%20Insider%20found%20hundreds%20related%20to%20loan%20transfers%2C%20missing%20or%20erroneous%20documentation%2C%20or%20confusion%20about%20obtaining%20payment%20status%20updates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20always%20very%20transparent%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20some%20transfers%20can%20involve%20%26quot%3Bobfuscation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Richard%20Gaudreau%2C%20a%20New%20Hampshire%20bankruptcy%20lawyer%20who%20represents%20borrowers%20in%20student-loan%20default%20lawsuits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EConfusing%20communication%20doesn't%20necessarily%20mean%20wrongdoing%2C%20said%20Simon%20Goldenberg%2C%20a%20New%20York%20debt-relief%20lawyer.%20While%20private%20lenders%20%26quot%3Bcould%20do%20a%20much%20better%20job%20at%20communicating%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20right%20way%20and%20the%20legal%20way%20are%20not%20always%20in%20sync.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECases%20like%20Carlson's%20could%20soon%20become%20more%20widespread.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-surprise-navient-trump-private-debt-repayment-overhaul-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPrivate%20lenders%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20expecting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-surprise-navient-trump-private-debt-repayment-overhaul-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20influx%20of%20borrowers%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-student-loan-debt-repayment-overhaul-final-rule-new-plans-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esweeping%20repayment%20overhaul%3C%2Fa%3E%20takes%20effect%20in%20July%2C%20bringing%20less%20generous%20repayment%20plans%20for%20federal%20borrowers%20and%20new%20caps%20on%20borrowing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrumps-student-loan-debt-repayment-overhaul-borrowing-caps-professional-degrees-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efor%20advanced%20degrees%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEllen%20Keast%2C%20the%20Department%20of%20Education's%20press%20secretary%20for%20higher%20education%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20White%20House%20expects%20colleges%20to%20lower%20their%20tuition%20in%20response.%20College%20sticker%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fresearch.collegeboard.org%2Ftrends%2Fcollege-pricing%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprices%20have%20doubled%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20last%2030%20years%2C%20per%20the%20College%20Board%2C%20at%20both%20public%20and%20private%20colleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20goal%2C%20Keast%20said%2C%20is%20to%20rein%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bout-of-control%20student-loan%20borrowing%20bonanza%20that%20encouraged%20institutions%20to%20inflate%20tuition%20and%20allowed%20students%20to%20take%20on%20absurd%20levels%20of%20debt%2C%20sometimes%20borrowing%20beyond%20their%20means%20to%20repay.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dc675d79-bad1-44b3-a5e8-710d26204ea3%5C%22%3EThe%20cost%20of%20confusion%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20communicating%20with%20borrowers%2C%20lenders%20must%20comply%20with%20a%201977%20law%20that%20governs%20when%20and%20how%20often%20they%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecan%20contact%20borrowers%2C%20and%20requires%20lenders%20to%20obtain%20consent%20before%20communicating%20outside%20usual%20hours.%20Failure%20to%20comply%20can%20bring%20fines%2C%20litigation%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-getting-checks-navient-settlement-cfpb-debt-relief-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eor%20federal%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eenforcement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20SoFi%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bcommunicates%20extensively%20with%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20by%20offering%20deferrals%20and%20payment%20extensions.%20%26quot%3BThese%20measures%20can%20help%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20struggling%20borrowers%20avoid%20further%20loan%20delinquency%20or%20default%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20all%2C%20making%20sure%20loans%20are%20paid%20back%20is%20good%20for%20business%2C%20said%20Scott%20Buchanan%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Student%20Loan%20Servicing%20Alliance%2C%20a%20private%20lenders'%20trade%20association.%20It's%20common%20practice%20to%20send%20delinquency%20notices%20by%20phone%2C%20email%2C%20and%20physical%20mail%2C%20and%20those%20notices%20typically%20escalate%20as%20a%20borrower%20nears%20default.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ashley%20Carlson%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fa2aae38bee05c9698405d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECarlson%20has%20denied%20SoFi's%20settlement%20offers%20and%20said%20she%20will%20continue%20fighting%20her%20lender%20in%20court.%3Cp%3EHannah%20Latham%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Carlson%20stopped%20making%20full%20payments%20on%20her%20loan%2C%20she%20defaulted.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAt%20this%20stage%2C%20lenders%20may%20pursue%20collections%20or%20litigation%2C%20either%20in-house%20or%20through%20third%20parties.%20As%20records%20change%20hands%2C%20they%20can%20become%20difficult%20to%20track%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20including%20for%20regulatory%20purposes%20%E2%80%94%20and%20borrowers%20might%20lose%20access%20to%20their%20original%20accounts%2C%20leaving%20them%20confused%20as%20to%20whether%20they%20still%20owe%20payments%20and%20to%20whom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarlson%20said%20she%20wasn't%20notified%20that%20SoFi%20had%20transferred%20her%20loan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20SoFi%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20%26quot%3BCongrats!%26quot%3B%20email%20was%20mistakenly%20generated%20by%20the%20company's%20marketing%20platform%20and%20did%20not%20absolve%20Carlson%20of%20any%20payment%20obligations.%20The%20company%20said%20it%20had%20previously%20called%20and%20emailed%20Carlson%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-defaulted-student-loan-borrowers-avoid-wage-social-security-garnishment-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoptions%20for%20curing%3C%2Fa%3E%20her%20delinquency%2C%20and%20that%20a%20third%20party%20handled%20further%20outreach%20after%20she%20defaulted.%20SoFi%20maintained%20ownership%20of%20the%20loan%20throughout%20the%20process%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarlson%20said%20she%20never%20received%20any%20communications%20before%20or%20after%20the%20%26quot%3BCongrats!%26quot%3B%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoFi%20did%20not%20provide%20Business%20Insider%20with%20documentation%20of%20any%20such%20outreach%20and%20declined%20to%20identify%20Carlson's%20third-party%20servicer%2C%20saying%20it%20cannot%20share%20details%20on%20account-level%20communications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20story%20is%20part%20of%20a%20new%20Business%20Insider%20series%2C%20%26quot%3BStudent%20debt%20spiral%2C%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20growing%20private%20student-loan%20industry.%20Stay%20tuned%20for%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShare%20your%20private%20student-loan%20experience%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3A%2520asheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20securely%20on%20Signal%20at%20asheffey.97.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20a%20loan%20enters%20default%2C%20communication%20might%20drop%20off%20and%20could%20come%20from%20either%20the%20lender%20or%20a%20third%20party%20that%20takes%20over%20the%20account%2C%20Goldenberg%20said%2C%20and%20the%20borrower%20might%20not%20recognize%20the%20sender.%20After%20that%20point%2C%20a%20lender%20could%20choose%20to%20keep%20the%20borrower's%20account%20viewable%20or%20block%20their%20access%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ecases%2C%20the%20matter%20may%20proceed%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eto%20litigation.%20A%20report%20from%20the%20advocacy%20group%20Protect%20Borrowers%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprotectborrowers.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F03%2FDubious-Debts_2021.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethat%20private%20lenders%20sued%3C%2Fa%3E%20more%20than%20100%2C000%20defaulted%20borrowers%20nationwide%20between%202012%20and%202016%2C%20the%20most%20recent%20period%20for%20which%20data%20are%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrivate%20student%20loans%20make%20up%20about%2010%25%20of%20the%20%241.85%20trillion%20student-loan%20market%20in%202025%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.consumerfinance.gov%2Ff%2Fdocuments%2Fcfpb_pelo-annual-report_2026-01.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECFPB%20data.%3C%2Fa%3E%20In%20general%2C%20those%20borrowers%20are%20in%20stronger%20financial%20shape%20than%20federal%20borrowers.%20The%20federal%20student-loan%20portfolio%20has%20a%20nearly%2010%25%20default%20rate%2C%20according%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorkfed.org%2Fmicroeconomics%2Ftopics%2Fstudent-debt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20New%20York%20as%20of%20late%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20comparison%2C%203.5%25%20of%20private-loan%20borrowers%20were%20in%20early-stage%20delinquency%20in%20late%202025%20(typically%20up%20to%20three%20months%20past%20due)%2C%201.7%25%20were%20near%20default%2C%20and%202.7%25%20had%20been%20charged%20off%20%E2%80%94%20an%20accounting%20move%20that%20happens%20after%20a%20default%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20Enterval%20Analytics%2C%20which%20provides%20insights%20on%20student-loan%20lenders.%20The%20report%20is%20based%20on%20data%20provided%20by%20major%20private%20lenders%2C%20including%20Sallie%20Mae%2C%20SoFi%2C%20and%20Navient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lack%20of%20clear%2C%20consistent%20communication%20is%20a%20sticking%20point%20with%20private%20student-loan%20borrowers.%20About%20one%20in%20four%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consumerfinance.gov%2Fcomplaint%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudent-loan%20complaints%3C%2Fa%3E%20ever%20filed%20with%20the%20CFPB%20is%20about%20private%20loans.%20In%202025%2C%2058%25%20of%20those%20complaints%20were%20focused%20on%20challenges%20dealing%20with%20lenders%2C%20including%20communication%20difficulties%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.consumerfinance.gov%2Ff%2Fdocuments%2Fcfpb_pelo-annual-report_2026-01.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJanuary%20CFPB%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20report%20said%20borrowers%20are%20often%20dealing%20with%20%26quot%3Bconfusion%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20transparency%2C%20or%20a%20lack%20of%20responsiveness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2258b9017f-a85d-4c58-a113-194b8fe8ace8%5C%22%3EWhen%20confusion%20becomes%20a%20crisis%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHannah%20Bates%2C%2030%2C%20took%20out%20%2455%2C000%20in%20private%20student%20loans%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-student-loan-repayment-overhaul-limits-for-nurses-public-comment-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efor%20nursing%20school%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019.%20She%20never%20anticipated%20that%20six%20years%20later%2C%20she%20would%20be%20representing%20herself%20in%20court%20after%20being%20sued%20by%20her%20lender%2C%20Sallie%20Mae.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20tabindex%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20data-media-container%3D%5C%22image%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22img%5C%22%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-figure-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cimg%20data-content-type%3D%5C%22image%2Fjpeg%5C%22%20data-srcs%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Bhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fa28c5b3045b292f636f81%26quot%3B%3A%7B%26quot%3BcontentType%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bimage%2Fjpeg%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3BaspectRatioW%26quot%3B%3A4160%2C%26quot%3BaspectRatioH%26quot%3B%3A5200%7D%7D%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fa28c5b3045b292f636f81width%3D1300%26amp%3Bformat%3Djpeg%26amp%3Bauto%3Dwebp%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hannah%20Bates%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%220%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%5Cn%3Cfigcaption%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-caption%5C%22%3E%5CnHannah%20Bates%20said%20she%20was%20unable%20to%20get%20clear%20answers%20on%20her%20account%20status%20when%20she%20defaulted%20on%20her%20private%20student%20loans.%C2%A0%5Cn%3Cspan%20data-e2e-name%3D%5C%22image-source%5C%22%3E%5CnNic%20Antaya%20for%20BI%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trouble%20began%20after%20she%20graduated%20in%202022%20and%20took%20a%20nursing%20job%20in%20Michigan.%20Bates%20said%20that%20her%20%2445%2C000%20annual%20salary%20wouldn't%20cover%20her%20%241%2C500%20loan%20payments%2C%20and%20that%20Sallie%20Mae%20denied%20her%20request%20for%20a%20more%20manageable%20monthly%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20doing%20my%20best%20for%20as%20long%20as%20I%20could%2C%26quot%3B%20Bates%20said.%20%26quot%3BBy%20no%20means%20am%20I%20not%20trying%20to%20pay%20you%20guys%20what%20I%20know%20I%20owe%20you%2C%20but%20I%20can't%20make%20these%20payments%20at%20this%20number.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBates%20began%20paying%20what%20she%20could%20%E2%80%94%20around%20%24560%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%20and%20slid%20into%20delinquency.%20She%20said%20communications%20from%20Sallie%20Mae%20were%20confusing%2C%20like%20a%202024%20email%20that%20read%20%26quot%3BCongratulations!%20We%20received%20the%20final%20payment%20on%20your%20loan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20that%20was%20wrong%2C%20so%20I%20called%20Sallie%20Mae%2C%20and%20they%20told%20me%20there%20was%20a%20glitch%20in%20the%20system%20and%20I%20probably%20got%20emailed%20by%20accident%2C%26quot%3B%20Bates%20said.%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20make%20an%20accident%20on%20something%20that%20big%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20two%20months%20later%2C%20she%20received%20a%20warning%20that%20her%20account%20was%20near%20default.%20Bates%20said%20she%20immediately%20called%20her%20account%20manager%20and%20asked%20if%20she%20could%20make%20a%20payment%20to%20avoid%20that%20outcome.%20She%20was%20advised%20to%20make%20a%20lump-sum%20payment%20to%20stop%20the%20default%20process%2C%20Bates%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20made%20the%20payment%20over%20the%20phone%20that%20same%20day.%20It%20was%20processed%2C%20Bates%20said%2C%20but%20her%20account%20status%20didn't%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20get%20someone%20new%20on%20the%20phone%2C%20and%20they're%20like%2C%20'Sorry%2C%20you're%20done.%20We've%20defaulted%20you%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20gave%20me%20no%20information%20on%20where%20that%20payment%20went%2C%20what%20was%20going%20to%20happen%20next.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224928%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Legal%20notice%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fa27fa405e0cf89dc873d7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223285%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBates%20said%20that%20conflicting%20information%20from%20Sallie%20Mae%20made%20it%20difficult%20to%20reverse%20her%20default%20status.%3Cp%3ENic%20Antaya%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBates%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrower-survey-save-debt-relief-repayment-forgiveness-trump-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethat%20conflicting%20information%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Sallie%20Mae%20made%20it%20difficult%20to%20reverse%20her%20default%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Sallie%20Mae%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bcustomer%20success%20is%20core%20to%20our%20mission%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20fewer%20than%203%25%20of%20Sallie%20Mae%20loans%20in%20repayment%20default%20annually.%20The%20spokesperson%20added%20that%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bproactively%20and%20consistently%26quot%3B%20communicates%20with%20its%20customers%2C%20informing%20them%20when%20they%20default%2C%20when%20their%20defaulted%20loan%20is%20sold%2C%20and%20who%20the%20new%20owner%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20weeks%2C%20Bates%20said%2C%20Sallie%20Mae%20moved%20to%20collect%20the%20full%20balance%20and%20asked%20whether%20she%20could%20pay%20it%20in%20full%20or%20borrow%20money%20from%20family%20or%20friends.%20She%20didn't%20have%20the%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20months%20later%2C%20Sallie%20Mae%20sued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22618852bf-ae03-4958-9afe-610b50c4ac0f%5C%22%3EWhere%20confusion%20meets%20consequences%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECarlson%20and%20Bates%20said%20they%20could%20not%20afford%20legal%20representation%2C%20so%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuilt-ai-agent-job-boss-replacement-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econsulted%20artificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20trying%20to%20do%20whatever%20they%20need%20to%20do%2C%20and%20it's%20on%20me%20to%20figure%20out%20my%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20Bates%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20when%20you%20don't%20have%20an%20attorney%2C%20and%20you're%20doing%20this%20all%20%3Cem%3Epro%20se%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20it's%20so%20hard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20CFPB%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-internal-memo-cfpb-deprioritize-student-loans-medical-debt-trump-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeprioritizing%20student-loan%20oversight%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20the%20Trump%20administration%20and%20inconsistent%20student-loan%20protections%20across%20states%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20puts%20a%20lot%20more%20responsibility%20on%20the%20borrower%20to%20actually%20know%20what%20their%20rights%20are%20and%20where%20there%20are%20violations%20of%20those%20rights%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Julie%20Margetta%20Morgan%2C%20president%20of%20the%20think%20tank%20Century%20Foundation%20and%20a%20top%20official%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Education%20and%20the%20CFPB%20under%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiz%20Gilbert%2C%2045%2C%20fell%20behind%20on%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-private-debt-no-relief-interest-rates-payments-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprivate%20student-loan%20payments%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20said%20she%20felt%20%26quot%3Bfrustrated%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bstupid%26quot%3B%20while%20trying%20to%20get%20answers%20from%20her%20lender%20about%20the%20status%20of%20her%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJenna%20Zaccagnino%2C%2038%2C%20is%20getting%20letters%20warning%20that%20she's%20in%20serious%20delinquency%20on%20her%20private%20student%20loans%20and%20is%20at%20risk%20of%20litigation.%20She%20said%20that%20when%20she%20called%20her%20lender%20for%20help%20with%20making%20payments%2C%20she%20received%20conflicting%20information%2C%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bnobody%20knows%20what%20to%20do%26quot%3B%20because%20the%20holder%20of%20her%20loan%20keeps%20changing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227651%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hannah%20Bates%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb7182f9e4752b6d60169f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225101%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBates%20points%20to%20one%20of%20her%20defaulted%20student-loan%20balances%20that%20is%20part%20of%20Sallie%20Mae's%20lawsuit.%3Cp%3ENic%20Antaya%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMelinda%20Laszczynski%2C%2039%2C%20called%20Navient%20to%20see%20if%20she%20could%20lower%20her%20%241%2C900%20payments%2C%20to%20no%20avail.%20Navient%20eventually%20sold%20Laszczynski's%20loans%20to%20a%20debt%20collector%2C%20and%20while%20she%20received%20a%20notice%20that%20her%20account%20was%20charged%20off%20or%20transferred%20to%20a%20third%20party%2C%20she%20only%20discovered%20who%20that%20third%20party%20was%20when%20an%20agency%20she%20didn't%20recognize%20contacted%20her%20to%20collect%20her%20balance%20in%20full.%20One%20email%20from%20Assent%20Recovery%20Solutions%20had%20the%20subject%20line%3A%20%26quot%3BYour%20Account%20Qualifies%20for%20a%20Settlement!!!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20things%20happen%20in%20life%3B%20we%20want%20to%20help%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20email%20read.%20It%20included%20a%20link%20to%20an%20online%20payment%20portal%20to%20pay%20off%20her%20%24160%2C000%20balance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Navient%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20company%20follows%20the%20CFPB's%20loan%20transfer%20requirements%2C%20which%20include%20sending%20multiple%20notices%20before%20a%20transfer%2C%20and%20that%20the%20new%20servicer%20would%20send%20the%20borrower%20a%20welcome%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarlson's%20and%20Bates'%20litigation%20is%20ongoing.%20Carlson%20is%20awaiting%20a%20trial%2C%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBates%20is%20waiting%20to%20hear%20from%20Sallie%20Mae%20on%20the%20next%20steps.%20For%20Bates%2C%20those%20steps%20would%20likely%20be%20an%20agreement%20on%20a%20repayment%20plan%20that%20she%20can%20afford%20to%20return%20to%20good%20standing.%20Carlson%20has%20declined%20SoFi's%20settlement%20offers.%20If%20her%20push%20to%20discharge%20her%20loans%20fails%20in%20court%20and%20she%20doesn't%20make%20her%20payments%2C%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffive-years-student-debt-relief-suddenly-over-trump-default-collections-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewages%20could%20be%20garnished%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Bates'%20March%20hearing%2C%20Judge%20Annette%20Berry%20encouraged%20her%20to%20reach%20a%20resolution%20with%20the%20lender's%20attorney.%20Berry%20said%20during%20the%20hearing%20that%20cases%20like%20Bates'%20are%20a%20growing%20issue%20in%20her%20courtroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20seeing%20this%20happen%20more%20and%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Berry%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20going%20after%20people%20for%20unpaid%20student-loan%20debt.%20And%20so%20if%20you%20think%20you're%20the%20only%20one%2C%20you're%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBates%20hopes%20her%20story%20can%20serve%20as%20a%20lesson%20to%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20wish%20this%20on%20my%20worst%20enemy%2C%26quot%3B%20Bates%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20absolutely%20consuming%20my%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-communications-transfers-lawsuits-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778144461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb700d5edd94d1e7339d1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-communications-transfers-lawsuits-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Student-loan%20borrowers%20who%20fall%20behind%20can%20get%20trapped%20in%20a%20maze%20of%20confusing%20communications%20with%20private%20lenders.%20Sometimes%20it%20ends%20in%20lawsuits.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Consuming%20too%20much%20AI%20can%20be%20a%20bad%20idea.%20New%20data%20on%20'tokenmaxxing'%20reveals%20a%20better%20approach.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nathan's%20Hot%20Dog%20Eating%20champion%20Joey%20Chestnut%20eats%20an%20olive%20burgers%20before%20the%20Lugnuts%20game%20against%20the%20TinCaps%20at%20Jackson%20Field%20in%20Lansing.%20Chestnut%20set%20a%20record%20with%2013%20olive%20burgers%20eaten%20in%205%20minutes.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb927ce1443b8dc48e27be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221335%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EConsuming%20too%20much%20is%20sometimes%20not%20good.%20Burger%20consumption%20is%20shown%20above.%20AI%20token%20consumption%20is%20discussed%20below.%3Cp%3EUSA%20TODAY%20Network%20via%20Reuters%20Connect%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHeavy%20AI%20token%20consumption%20yields%20limited%20returns%2C%20Jellyfish%20found%20in%20a%20recent%20study.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJellyfish%20data%20shows%20top%20AI%20users%20consume%2010%20times%20as%20much%2C%20and%20output%20only%20doubles.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJellyfish%20AI%20head%20Nicholas%20Arcolano%20advises%20balanced%20AI%20use%20for%20productivity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tech%20industry%20is%20entering%20a%20new%20phase%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-feels-how-you-speak-inworld-kylan-gibbs-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20spending%20discipline%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20latest%20data%20from%20Jellyfish%20suggests%20the%20winners%20are%20not%20the%20biggest%20token%20burners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20study%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-coding-boom-more-software-shipped-no-hit-quality-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eengineering%20intelligence%20company%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EJellyfish%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20the%20top%2010%25%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ai-breakthrough-vibe-coding-revolution-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EClaude%20Code%3C%2Fa%3E%20users%20consumed%20about%2010%20times%20as%20many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-compute-compensation-software-engineers-greg-brockman-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20tokens%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20median%20developer%2C%20but%20produced%20only%20about%20twice%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20output.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jensen-huang-ai-factory-tokens-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20tokens%20are%20small%20chunks%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20text%20that%20AI%20models%20break%20words%20and%20inputs%20into%20to%20process%20them.%20They%20are%20also%20a%20way%20to%20price%20AI%20usage%2C%20usually%20at%20a%20cost%20per%20million%20tokens.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENicholas%20Arcolano%2C%20Jellyfish's%20head%20of%20AI%20and%20research%2C%20said%20that%20gap%20is%20the%20clearest%20sign%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftokenmaxxing-ai-token-leaderboards-debate-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eextreme%20%26quot%3Btokenmaxxing%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20workers%20use%20as%20many%20AI%20tokens%20as%20possible%2C%20is%20not%20a%20sustainable%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCFOs%20are%20getting%20on%20people's%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BIn%20most%20companies%2C%20you%20can't%20work%20without%20showing%20your%20receipts.%20Customers%20want%20to%20move%20fast%2C%20and%20they're%20willing%20to%20spend%20money%20here%2C%20but%20they%20can't%20do%20it%20without%20showing%20they're%20spending%20responsibly%20and%20having%20an%20impact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJellyfish%20has%20access%20to%20hundreds%20of%20companies%20and%20the%20coding%20behavior%20of%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20software%20engineers.%20It%20found%20that%20consuming%20a%20massive%20number%20of%20tokens%20may%20not%20always%20generate%20real%20returns%2C%20while%20increasing%20costs%20for%20companies.%20This%20is%20pushing%20the%20tech%20industry%20into%20a%20new%20phase%20in%20which%20AI%20efficiency%20is%20becoming%20more%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20you%20rationalize%20that%20you're%20getting%20more%20value%20from%20these%20things%20than%20you%20would%20get%20from%20a%20human%20doing%20the%20same%20work%2C%20if%20token%20costs%20surge%2C%20a%20CFO%20will%20still%20worry%20that%20you%20broke%20their%20spreadsheets%2C%26quot%3B%20Arcolano%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20the%20Jellyfish%20report%20shows%20how%20quickly%20token%20use%20can%20scale%20at%20the%20high%20end.%20Weekly%20Claude%20Code%20consumption%20for%20top%20AI%20adopters%20reached%20225%20million%20tokens%20per%20user%2C%20compared%20to%2032%20million%20for%20the%20median%20software%20engineer%20tracked%20by%20Jellyfish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22890%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20chart%20from%20Jellyfish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb9a90e1443b8dc48e2814%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22775%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20chart%20from%20Jellyfish.%3Cp%3EJellyfish%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20AI%20adoption%20was%20associated%20with%20more%20productivity%2C%20measured%20in%20pull%20requests%2C%20a%20common%20measure%20of%20code%20output.%20Very%20high-adoption%20teams%20posted%2077%25%20more%20pull%20request%20throughput%20than%20low-adoption%20teams%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20data%20from%20Jellyfish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EArcolano%20said%20raw%20token%20volume%20is%20too%20messy%20to%20use%20on%20its%20own%20as%20a%20productivity%20score.%20AI%20model%20changes%20can%20cause%20token%20counts%20to%20swing%20dramatically%20even%20when%20behavior%20does%20not%20change%2C%20meaning%20a%20developer's%20token%20spend%20is%20not%20always%20a%20reliable%20proxy%20for%20true%20productivity.%20Instead%2C%20he%20said%20leaders%20should%20track%20cost%20per%20pull%20request%20or%20another%20outcome-based%20metric%2C%20not%20token%20totals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20heavy%20AI%20use%20can%20help%2C%20but%20only%20to%20a%20point.%20The%20company's%20data%20indicates%20that%20highly%20active%20users%2C%20who%20often%20tap%20AI%20agents%20to%20help%20with%20coding%2C%20are%20more%20productive%20on%20average%2C%20yet%20the%20returns%20are%20not%20proportional%20to%20the%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRather%20than%20think%20ahead%20about%20the%20right%20way%20to%20do%20something%2C%20I'll%20have%20five%20AI%20agents%20build%20it%20five%20different%20ways%20and%20pick%20the%20winner%2C%26quot%3B%20Arcolano%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I'm%20throwing%20away%20a%20lot%20of%20work.%20It's%20probably%20effective%20and%20still%20cheaper%20than%20a%20person%20doing%20it%2C%20but%20it's%20more%20expensive%20than%20just%20doing%20it%20one%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Arcolano's%20view%2C%20the%20best%20path%20is%20to%20push%20AI%20coding%20adoption%20broadly%2C%20get%20more%20engineers%20into%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20curve%2C%20and%20avoid%20both%20underuse%20and%20extreme%20overconsumption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20middle%20ground%20is%20where%20AI%20becomes%20a%20durable%20operating%20advantage%3A%20enough%20usage%20to%20drive%20real%20shipping%20gains%2C%20but%20not%20so%20much%20that%20teams%20burn%20money%20chasing%20marginal%20output.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20my%20mum%20always%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BEverything%20in%20moderation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20out%20to%20me%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabarr%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabarr%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-tokenmaxxing-fails-as-productivity-strategy-jellyfish-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778144401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb928b3cfefc31768d64af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-tokenmaxxing-fails-as-productivity-strategy-jellyfish-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jellyfish%20data%20shows%20that%20while%20AI%20%26quot%3Btokenmaxxing%26quot%3B%20boosts%20coding%20output%2C%20extreme%20token%20use%20delivers%20diminishing%20returns%20for%20companies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abarr%40businessinsider.com%20(Alistair%20Barr)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Local%20data%20center%20opposition%20claims%20its%20latest%20victim%3A%20Oracle's%20Project%20Jupiter%20gas%20plant%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228192%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Data%20Center%20Box%20Elder%20County%20Protest%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb773e5edd94d1e7339d4c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225464%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EData%20centers%20are%20facing%20rising%20opposition%20from%20local%20communities.%3Cp%3ENatalie%20Behring%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOracle%20dropped%20its%20plans%20for%20a%20natural%20gas%20plant%20at%20its%20OpenAI%20data%20center%20in%20New%20Mexico.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20gas%20plant%20raised%20questions%20from%20the%20surrounding%20community%20about%20water%20use%20and%20air%20pollution.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECommunity%20activists%20aren't%20yet%20convinced%20of%20the%20site's%20new%20energy%20plan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOracle%20is%20ditching%20a%20contentious%20plan%20to%20construct%20a%20natural%20gas%20plant%20to%20power%20one%20of%20its%20newest%20data%20centers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Oracle%20said%20last%20week%20that%20it%20will%20partner%20with%20fuel-cell%20maker%20Bloom%20Energy%20to%20generate%20on-site%20electricity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDubbed%20Project%20Jupiter%2C%20the%20site%20in%20New%20Mexico%20is%20part%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftexas-stargate-data-center-build-cost-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOracle%20and%20OpenAI's%3C%2Fa%3E%20%24300%20billion%20cloud%20computing%20contract.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProject%20Jupiter's%20potential%20environmental%20impact%20has%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20intense%20scrutiny%20and%20speculation%20by%20the%20local%20community%20for%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20release%20last%20week%2C%20the%20tech%20giant%20said%20Bloom's%20technology%20would%20%26quot%3Bdramatically%20reduce%20water%20use%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bprotect%20local%20air%20quality%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20data%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20abrupt%20change%20in%20plans%20is%20emblematic%20of%20the%20unpredictable%20nature%20of%20the%20AI%20infrastructure%20buildout.%20That%20unpredictability%20is%20only%20intensifying%20as%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-earnings-microsoft-ai-investment-capex-plan-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Tech%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0companies%20race%20to%20build%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-calculate-data-center-cost-environmental-impact-methodology-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20fight%20for%20increasingly%20scarce%20electricity%C2%A0resources%20to%20power%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody's%20trying%20to%20build%20capacity%20to%20meet%20this%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Patrick%20Hughes%2C%20senior%20vice%20president%20of%20industry%20affairs%20at%20the%20National%20Electrical%20Manufacturers%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHughes%20called%20the%20pace%20of%20data%20center%20construction%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented%26quot%3B%20and%20likened%20the%20AI%20race%20and%20power%20scramble%20to%20the%20Wild%20West.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f2ff59e5-8d32-4835-9a54-25125cf1959a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBring%20your%20own%20power%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUtilities%20across%20the%20country%20have%20been%20overwhelmed%20with%20requests%20from%20data%20centers%20to%20connect%20to%20the%20grid.%20Rather%20than%20risk%20yearslong%20waits%20to%20come%20online%2C%20many%20developers%20are%20turning%20to%20%26quot%3BBYOP%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-centers-on-site-power-plants-trump-announces-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebring%20your%20own%20power%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20planning%20to%20self-supply%20electricity%20on-site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOracle%20is%20betting%20big%20on%20BYOP.%20Besides%20Project%20Jupiter%2C%20the%20company%20has%20announced%20plans%20to%20build%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-building-natural-gas-microgrid-at-new-texas-data-center-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20gas%20plants%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20two%20of%20its%20other%20data%20center%20projects%20with%20OpenAI.%20Both%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftexas-power-grid-demand-data-centers-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elocated%20in%20Texas%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20October%2C%20Project%20Jupiter%20developers%20filed%20air%20quality%20permit%20applications%20for%20a%20natural%20gas%20plant%20with%20the%20New%20Mexico%20Environment%20Department.%20The%20applications%20were%20still%20pending%20when%20they%20were%20withdrawn%20on%20April%2027%2C%20according%20to%20NMED's%20online%20records%20database.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20release%20last%20week%2C%20Oracle%20cited%20its%20commitment%20to%20%26quot%3Bcommunity%20priorities%26quot%3B%20and%20touted%20Bloom's%20technology%2C%20which%20it%20said%20will%20help%20reduce%20the%20data%20center's%20water%20use%20and%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHughes%20couldn't%20speak%20to%20Oracle's%20canceled%20natural%20gas%20project%2C%20though%20he%20said%20data%20centers%20that%20want%20to%20build%20their%20own%20power%20plants%20face%20a%20litany%20of%20constraints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20balance%20supply%20chain%20concerns%20and%20availability%2C%20the%20cost%2C%20the%20speed%20at%20which%20you%20can%20get%20the%20permits%20and%20build%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228dd400cf-e4c5-4fe3-a1fe-c058ec64590b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOracle's%20Project%20Jupiter%20faces%20opposition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EProject%20Jupiter%20had%20been%20snagged%20by%20federal%20and%20state%20regulators%20in%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20cancellation%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%20and%20April%2C%20both%20the%20Federal%20Energy%20Regulatory%20Commission%20and%20the%20New%20Mexico%20State%20Land%20Office%20denied%20requests%20related%20to%20a%20proposed%20natural%20gas%20pipeline%20that%20would%20deliver%20fuel%20to%20Project%20Jupiter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocal%20pushback%20has%20also%20become%20an%20issue.%20Across%20the%20country%2C%20opposition%20to%20data%20centers%20has%20grown%20as%20local%20communities%20protest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foracle-open-ai-data-center-michigan-power-rates-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erising%20power%20bills%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-center-noise-disruptions-loudoun-county-virginia-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enoise%20pollution%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20the%20use%20of%20local%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20NMED%20said%20it%20would%20need%20to%20schedule%20a%20public%20hearing%20to%20address%20the%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%26quot%3B%20amount%20of%20comments%20it%20received%20regarding%20the%20Project%20Jupiter%20gas%20plant.%20The%20agency%20said%20it%20had%20received%20more%20than%207%2C000%20comments%20on%20Project%20Jupiter's%20permit%20applications%2C%20many%20of%20them%20regarding%20the%20plant's%20potential%20impact%20on%20water%20use%20and%20air%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20hearing%2C%20scheduled%20for%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6a80f35-f620-430a-8a1e-c27c29f56fb5%5C%22%3EOracle's%20data%20center%20faces%20environmental%20concerns%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EProject%20Jupiter%20also%20faces%20two%20lawsuits%20brought%20by%20the%20New%20Mexico%20Environmental%20Law%20Center%20on%20behalf%20of%20local%20activists.%20NMELC%20says%20the%20officials%20approved%20the%20data%20center%20before%20crucial%20environmental%2C%20water%2C%20and%20community-impact%20assessments%20were%20conducted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20a%20New%20Mexico%20state%20court%20struck%20down%20the%20county's%20request%20to%20dismiss%20the%20initial%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20NMELC%20staff%20attorney%20Kacey%20Hovden%20questioned%20the%20reasoning%20behind%20Project%20Jupiter's%20sudden%20decision%20to%20pivot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20say%20they're%20responding%20to%20community%20concerns%2C%20but%20these%20have%20been%20things%20that%20have%20been%20voiced%20now%20for%20almost%20a%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Hovden%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20didn't%20they%20do%20this%20in%20the%20beginning%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENMELC%20has%20the%20same%20concerns%20about%20Bloom%20Energy's%20fuel%20cell%20technology%20as%20it%20had%20about%20the%20natural%20gas%20plant%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20want%20to%20be%20misconstrued%2C%26quot%3B%20Hovden%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20isn't%20a%20smart%20choice%20for%20public%20health%20either.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFuel%20cells%20can%20be%20powered%20by%20various%20fuels%2C%20though%20most%20use%20hydrogen%20derived%20from%20natural%20gas.%20Project%20Jupiter's%20fuel%20cells%20will%20use%20natural%20gas%2C%20according%20to%20new%20permit%20applications%20filed%20with%20NMED%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBloom%20Energy%20contends%20that%20its%20technology%20helps%20reduce%20emissions%20from%20natural%20gas%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20fuel%20cell%20technology%20has%20not%20been%20deployed%20at%20the%20scale%20required%20by%20a%20data%20center%20like%20Project%20Jupiter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOracle%20said%20its%20partnership%20with%20Bloom%20Energy%20could%20power%20its%20data%20center%20with%20up%20to%202.8%20gigawatts%20of%20electricity%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3Eenough%20to%20power%20more%20than%202%20million%20homes%2C%20or%20over%207%2C000%20Tesla%20Model%203s%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.energy.gov%2Fcmei%2Farticles%2Fhow-much-power-1-gigawatt%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDepartment%20of%20Energy%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20Bloom%20Energy's%20biggest%20data%20center%20partnership%20to%20date.%20In%202024%2C%20Bloom%20announced%20an%2080%20megawatt%20project%20in%20South%20Korea%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tiny%20fraction%20of%20Project%20Jupiter's%20scale.%20In%20a%20press%20release%20at%20the%20time%2C%20Bloom%20said%20it%20would%20be%20the%20%26quot%3Bworld's%20largest%20fuel%20cell%20installation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foracle-cancels-project-jupiter-gas-plant-amid-local-pushback-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778144401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fb79d33cfefc31768d63c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foracle-cancels-proje