26050700740_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22RECPDCL%20has%20invited%20bids%20for%20two%20interstate%20transmission%20projects%20to%20evacuate%20power%20from%2021.5%20GW%20renewable%20energy%20capacity%20planned%20across%20Gujarat%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Frecpdcl-launches-transmission-tenders-for-gujarat-renewable-projects-126050700740_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Frecpdcl-launches-transmission-tenders-for-gujarat-renewable-projects-126050700740_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Frecpdcl-launches-transmission-tenders-for-gujarat-renewable-projects-126050700740_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chipotle's%20CEO%20says%20customers%20can%20just%20ask%20for%20extra%20food.%20I%20put%20it%20to%20the%20test.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223144%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20a%20Chipotle%20storefront.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fbc9bc3cfefc31768d6686%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221769%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20tested%20Chipotle's%20portion%20sizes%20after%20its%20CEO%20said%20customers%20should%20%26quot%3Bjust%20ask%26quot%3B%20for%20more%20food.%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChipotle's%20CEO%20went%20viral%20this%20week%20after%20saying%20customers%20should%20ask%20for%20more%20food%20if%20they%20want%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20went%20to%20three%20different%20locations%20to%20put%20his%20promise%20of%20%26quot%3Babundance%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20test.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20found%20that%20portion%20sizes%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20whether%20you%20can%20get%20extra%20add-ons%20for%20free%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0depend%20on%20who%20you%20ask.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20Chipotle%20employee%20I%20spoke%20to%20started%20scooping%20more%20steak%20into%20my%20bowl%20before%20I%20could%20finish%20my%20sentence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCan%20I%20get%20a%20little%20extra%20meat%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithout%20hesitation%2C%20the%20worker%20reached%20for%20another%20full%20scoop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20stopped%20her%20midway%20through.%20I%20wasn't%20actually%20trying%20to%20order%20my%20bowl%20%26quot%3Bdouble%20protein%26quot%3B%20style.%20I%20was%20testing%20a%20claim%20made%20this%20week%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchipotle-price-changes-core-customer-shaped-economy-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChipotle%20CEO%20Scott%20Boatwright%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20after%20years%20of%20complaints%20that%20the%20chain's%20portions%20have%20gotten%20stingier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20should%20ask%20for%20a%20little%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20Boatwright%20said%20on%20Yahoo%20Finance's%20%26quot%3BPower%20Players%26quot%3B%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAbundance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bhas%20always%20been%20our%20brand%20ethos%2C%20and%20it%20is%20still%20to%20this%20day%3A%20We%20serve%20big%2C%20beautiful%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchipotle-new-menu-items-global-flavors-after-sales-stumble-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebowls%20and%20burritos%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20full%20stop%2C%20no%20questions%20asked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20more%2C%20just%20ask%20the%20team%20member%2C%26quot%3B%20Boatwright%20said%20in%20a%20clip%20that%20has%20since%20gone%20viral.%20%26quot%3BI%20promise%20you%2C%20there's%20never%20a%20team%20member%20on%20that%20line%20who's%20going%20to%20say%20no%20to%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20on%20Wednesday%20afternoon%2C%20I%20visited%20three%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchipotle-serious-politics-new-pac-federal-donations-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChipotle%20locations%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20California%20to%20see%20what%20would%20happen%20if%20I%20asked%20for%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20dining%20room%20of%20a%20Chipotle%20store%20during%20a%20lunch%20rush.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fbca3be1443b8dc48e29c3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20lunch%20rush%20found%20the%20dining%20room%20nearly%20full%2C%20with%20a%20long%20line%20of%20customers%20waiting%20for%20their%20to-go%20orders.%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20answer%3A%20It%20depends%20on%20what%20you're%20asking%20for%2C%20who's%20behind%20the%20counter%2C%20and%20how%20much%20food%20the%20store%20has%20left%20that%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20all%20three%20locations%2C%20workers%20told%20me%20the%20same%20thing%3A%20Customers%20can%20ask%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchipotle-portion-size-inconsistencies-robots-automation-human-employees-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eextra%20portions%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20non-premium%20ingredients%20like%20rice%2C%20beans%2C%20fajita%20veggies%2C%20corn%20salsa%2C%20cheese%2C%20and%20lettuce%20without%20being%20charged%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProtein%2C%20guacamole%2C%20and%20queso%20are%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22rgba(0%2C%200%2C%200%2C%200)%5C%22%3EWhen%20reached%20for%20comment%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20a%20Chipotle%20spokesperson%20reiterated%20the%20policy.%20The%20chain's%20new%20cilantro%20lime%20sauce%20is%20also%20extra%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fmark%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20Chipotle%2C%20our%20intentions%20are%20to%20provide%20a%20great%20guest%20experience%20every%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Laurie%20Schalow%2C%20chief%20corporate%20affairs%20officer%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20That's%20why%20guests%20can%20%26quot%3Bvocalize%20or%20digitally%20select%20their%20desired%20portions%26quot%3B%20of%20all%20non-premium%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b185dad3-1d9b-4eb4-84b0-dfb1ec9e3bed%5C%22%3ESanta%20Barbara%2C%20California%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20first%20location%2C%20after%20I%20identified%20myself%20as%20a%20reporter%2C%20a%20manager%20stepped%20in%20to%20explain%20the%20policy%20and%20why%20I'd%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20a%20second%20helping%20of%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esteak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20can%20give%20customers%20more%20of%20%26quot%3Banything%20other%20than%20protein%2C%20guacamole%2C%20or%20queso%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%20Since%20those%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchipotle-courts-gen-z-new-dorm-room-merchandise-loyalty-program-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epremium%20items%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20come%20with%20a%20surcharge%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0usually%20an%20additional%20%3Cmark%20data-color%3D%5C%22rgba(0%2C%200%2C%200%2C%200)%5C%22%3E%242.50%20to%20%244.10%20per%20entr%C3%A9e%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20item.%3C%2Fmark%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20manager%20said%20she'd%20seen%20clips%20of%20Boatwright's%20comments%20circulating%20online%20and%20expected%20the%20issue%20to%20come%20up%20during%20a%20regional%20meeting%20later%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20employees%20working%20the%20line%20chimed%20in%20to%20say%20they'd%20seen%20the%20video%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Chipotle%20staff%20member%20adds%20lettuce%20to%20a%20burrito%20bowl.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fbca84c9dd4cb81cda7eaf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Chipotle%20staff%20who%20spoke%20to%20Business%20Insider%20said%20adherence%20to%20their%20%26quot%3Bextras%26quot%3B%20policy%20varies%20slightly%20depending%20on%20who%20is%20working%20the%20line.%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20manager%20said%20customers%20occasionally%20ask%20for%20extra%20portions%2C%20but%20she%20expects%20more%20people%20to%20start%20doing%20so%20since%20Boatwright's%20comments%20have%20spread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229f5fd0db-37bd-4d8b-a837-e6a0b0ba80d7%5C%22%3EOxnard%2C%20California%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20second%20location%2C%20I%20watched%20the%20customer%20ahead%20of%20me%20ask%20for%20extra%20cheese%20with%20no%20pushback.%20Another%20customer%20got%20more%20rice%20on%20her%20tacos%20without%20any%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20my%20turn%2C%20a%20server%20again%20reiterated%20the%20same%20policy%3A%20Extra%20portions%20of%20non-premium%20ingredients%20were%20fine%2C%20the%20rest%20came%20with%20a%20charge.%20I%20was%20given%20more%20fajita%20vegetables%20and%20corn%20salsa%20with%20no%20additional%20questions%20or%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmployees%20there%20also%20said%20the%20ongoing%20online%20discourse%20around%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchipotle-customers-eating-less-beef-going-for-chicken-instead-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChipotle%20portions%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20made%20their%20jobs%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20just%20how%20it%20goes%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20worker%20said%20after%20describing%20how%20upset%20customers%20have%20become%20about%20portions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20employee%20said%20the%20store's%20chicken%20supply%20had%20recently%20been%20running%20low%2C%20forcing%20staff%20to%20be%20more%20conservative%20with%20servings.%20While%20most%20customers%20are%20polite%2C%20she%20said%20she%20worries%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eabout%20the%20anger%20she%20sees%20online%20spilling%20into%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22120f2dac-4dd5-49fd-9423-325f59764143%5C%22%3EVentura%2C%20California%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20Chipotle%20I%20visited%20was%20much%20quieter%20as%20I%20entered%20after%20the%20lunch%20rush.%20Employees%20were%20more%20candid%20about%20how%20much%20discretion%20individual%20stores%20%E2%80%94%20and%20managers%20%E2%80%94%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20worker%20told%20me%20employees%20are%20trained%20during%20onboarding%20to%20start%20with%20a%20standard%20serving%20size%20and%20provide%20more%20non-premium%20ingredients%20if%20customers%20ask.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20employees%20I%20spoke%20with%20said%20that%20how%20strictly%20the%20policy%20is%20enforced%20often%20depends%20on%20management.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20ingredients%20are%20running%20low%2C%20for%20example%2C%20grill%20cooks%20or%20managers%20may%20tell%20workers%20to%20%26quot%3Bwatch%20your%20portions%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20employee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20location%2C%20workers%20said%20managers%20were%20fairly%20relaxed%20about%20extra%20portions%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20for%20premium%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20no%20big%20deal%20to%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20employee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20workers%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchipotle-less-gen-z-millennial-customers-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecustomer%20complaints%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20portion%20sizes%20are%20constant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20come%20in%20mad%20all%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20other%20echoed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20they'd%20noticed%20more%20customers%20asking%20for%20extra%20food%20since%20Boatwright's%20comments%20started%20circulating%20online.%20While%20employees%20at%20their%20store%20haven't%20had%20major%20issues%20with%20angry%20customers%2C%20they%20said%20they%20heard%20workers%20at%20stricter%20locations%20are%20getting%20yelled%20at%20more%20frequently%20when%20they%20have%20to%20explain%20surcharge%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223451%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20Chipotle%20burrito%20bowls%20on%20a%20table%20with%20a%20bag%20of%20chips.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fbcd343cfefc31768d6690%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222588%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChipotle's%20portion%20sizes%20varied%20at%20each%20location.%3Cp%3EKatherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBoatwright's%20comments%20aren't%20the%20first%20time%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-ceo-brian-niccol-repeat-chipotle-strategy-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChipotle%20leadership%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20addressed%20portion%20complaints.%20Company%20executives%20have%20spent%20years%20pushing%20back%20against%20accusations%20that%20it%20has%20reduced%20serving%20sizes%2C%20while%20social%20media%20users%20regularly%20post%20videos%20criticizing%20skimpy%20meals%20alongside%20%26quot%3Bhacks%26quot%3B%20to%20get%20larger%20scoops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20kerfuffle%20is%20landing%20at%20a%20moment%20when%20the%20whole%20fast-casual%20bowl%20category%20is%20under%20pressure%20to%20justify%20its%20price%20tag.%20As%20Business%20Insider%20has%20reported%2C%20diners%20are%20getting%20more%20skeptical%20about%20the%20value%20of%20meals%20from%20chains%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaste-test-cava-chipotle-sweetgreen-slop-bowls-losing-sales-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChipotle%2C%20Cava%2C%20and%20Sweetgreen%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChipotle's%20April%2029%20earnings%20call%20underscored%20what's%20at%20stake%20with%20that%20debate.%20The%20company%20said%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202026%20represented%20a%20return%20to%20positive%20transaction%20growth%20after%20four%20quarters%20of%20declines%20last%20year.%20Executives%20in%20the%20call%20repeatedly%20underscored%20that%20%26quot%3Bgenerous%20portions%26quot%3B%20and%20pricing%20below%20inflation%20are%20the%20reasons%20guests%20are%20coming%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20spending%20an%20afternoon%20asking%20for%20extra%20food%20myself%2C%20my%20biggest%20takeaway%20wasn't%20that%20Boatwright%20got%20it%20wrong.%20It%20was%20that%20Chipotle's%20portion%20policy%20seems%20less%20like%20a%20hard%20rule%20and%20more%20like%20a%20sliding%20scale%20%E2%80%94%20one%20shaped%20by%20local%20managers%2C%20supply%20shortages%2C%20and%20whichever%20employee%20happens%20to%20be%20holding%20the%20spoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftest-chipotle-portions-ceo-scott-boatwright-customers-request-extra-servings-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778141461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69fbc9c5c9dd4cb81cda7eac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftest-chipotle-portions-ceo-scott-boatwright-customers-request-extra-servings-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I%20tested%20Chipotle's%20portion%20sizes%20after%20the%20CEO's%20viral%20comments%20and%20found%20that%20whether%20you%20can%20get%20extra%20add-ons%20for%20free%20depends%20on%20who%20you%20ask.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktl%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Look%20at%20Virat%20Kohli%E2%80%99%3A%20Sanjay%20questions%20Rohit%20and%20Suryakumar%20fitness%20standards%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1778141261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-130885620%2Cimgsize-102258.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Fipl-2026%2Fipl-2026-look-at-virat-kohli-sanjay-manjrekar-questions-rohit-sharma-suryakumar-yadav-fitness-standards%2Farticleshow%2F130885463.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20India%20batter%20Sanj