ng%20session%20this%20week%2C%20catapulting%20the%20index%20above%20the%20psychological%2062%2C000%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rally%20was%20fueled%20by%20gains%20in%20tech%20stocks%20and%20rising%20optimism%20that%20tensions%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20could%20cool%20following%20reports%20of%20progress%20toward%20a%20potential%20peace%20deal%20with%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20top%20performers%20were%20firms%20in%20the%20semiconductor%20supply%20chain%2C%20including%20Renesas%20Electronics%20and%20Ibiden%2C%20as%20investors%20continued%20piling%20into%20companies%20tied%20to%20the%20artificial%20intelligence%20boom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJapan's%20rally%20comes%20after%20a%20blistering%20run%20in%20global%20markets%20while%20the%20country%20was%20effectively%20offline%20from%20Monday%20through%20Wednesday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20and%20Nasdaq%20both%20climbed%20to%20fresh%20record%20highs%20this%20week%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsouth-korea-stock-market-samsung-1-trillion-club-ai-boom-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESouth%20Korea's%20stock%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20rallied%20sharply.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20equity%20investors%20are%20still%20looking%20to%20put%20money%20to%20work%20and%20are%20jumping%20on%20positive-sounding%20news%20from%20the%20Gulf%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20analysts%20at%20ING%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Wednesday.%20They%20added%20that%20the%20market%20reaction%20looks%20%26quot%3Ba%20little%20overblown.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20they%20said%20the%20broader%20market%20mood%20remains%20firmly%20risk-on%20as%20investors%20continue%20betting%20that%20the%20AI-driven%20tech%20rally%20has%20further%20room%20to%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20window%20of%20optimism%20on%20a%20peace%20deal%20has%20allowed%20money%20to%20flow%20back%20into%20equities%20%E2%80%94%20driven%20by%20the%20underlying%20conviction%20that%20the%20tech%20sector%20AI%20buildout%20will%20endure%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20ING's%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20in%20sentiment%20has%20also%20rippled%20through%20currency%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20dollar%2C%20which%20had%20strengthened%20during%20the%20recent%20geopolitical%20turmoil%20as%20investors%20sought%20safety%2C%20has%20softened%20this%20week%20as%20hopes%20for%20de-escalation%20grew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Japanese%20yen%20surged%20to%20a%2010-week%20high%2C%20trading%20near%20155%20per%20dollar%20on%20Wednesday.%20That%20followed%20days%20of%20sharp%20moves%20that%20reignited%20speculation%20about%20intervention%20from%20Japanese%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20speculation%20was%20first%20triggered%20days%20before%2C%20when%20the%20yen%20spiked%20to%20steady%20near%20the%20157%20after%20crossing%20the%20key%20160%20threshold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETokyo%20has%20not%20publicly%20confirmed%20any%20action%2C%20though%20Japanese%20officials%20have%20repeatedly%20warned%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-yen-currency-warnings-dollar-impact-usd-jpy-carry-trade-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Especulative%20moves%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20currency%20market%20in%20recent%20months.%20The%20yen%20has%20stayed%20roughly%207%25%20weaker%20against%20the%20dollar%20over%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnalysts%20at%20MUFG%20said%20any%20intervention%20efforts%20may%20now%20be%20increasingly%20tied%20to%20unpredictable%20geopolitical%20developments%20rather%20than%20purely%20domestic%20policy%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Japanese%20authorities%20are%20more%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20unpredictable%20factors%20than%20in%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Derek%20Halpenny%2C%20MUFG's%20head%20of%20research%20for%20global%20markets%20EMEA%2C%20wrote%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feurope-germany-japan-economy-markets-investment-op