%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202013%2C%20said%20the%20company%20is%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20deciding%20how%20productivity%20gains%20may%20change%20team%20structures%20or%20head%20count.%20But%20two%20other%20things%20come%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20top%20priority%20for%20us%20right%20now%20is%20definitely%20making%20sure%20that%20we%20can%20get%20all%20teams%20onto%20a%20single%20tech%20stack%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20second%20priority%20is%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20everyone%20in%20the%20company%2C%20not%20just%20the%20engineers%2C%20is%20as%20AI-capable%20as%20anyone%20else.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXu%20said%20that%20while%20DoorDash%20is%20delivering%20features%20and%20projects%20faster%2C%20customers%20hold%20the%20company%20to%20a%20much%20higher%20standard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20being%20more%20productive.%20We're%20shipping%20more%20code.%20But%20the%20ultimate%20question%20I%20have%20is%2C%20are%20we%20actually%20delivering%20better%20outcomes%20for%20customers%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXu's%20remarks%20differ%20from%20what%20many%20leaders%20are%20saying%20about%20the%20technology%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20tech%2C%20executives%20are%20touting%20AI-led%20productivity%20gains%20and%20saying%20that%20between%2050%25%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-president-ai-now-writing-80-percent-of-code-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E90%25%20of%20their%20code%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20now%20AI-generated.%20AI%20is%20also%20increasingly%20being%20cited%20as%20a%20reason%20for%20layoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20Australian-American%20software%20company%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatlassian-layoff-global-workforce-attributes-it-to-the-ai-era-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAtlassian%20announced%20it%20would%20cut%201%2C600%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20jobs%2C%20about%2010%25%20of%20its%20global