t%20Both%20Parents%20as%20a%20Teen%20but%2022-YO%20Rupam%20Kept%20Her%20Promise%20%26amp%3B%20Cleared%20JPSC%20in%201st%20Attempt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20quiet%20evening%20at%20the%20hospital%20in%20Ranchi%20when%20two%20sisters%20clutched%20their%20mother%E2%80%99s%20frail%20hands.%20Sixteen-year-old%20Rupam%20Sonali%20held%20her%20mother%E2%80%99s%20face%20gently%2C%20her%20eyes%20brimming%20with%20tears%20she%20refused%20to%20shed.%20Moments%20later%2C%20their%20world%20changed%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Rupam%20and%20her%20elder%20sister%20Rupali%2C%20life%20would%20never%20be%20the%20same%20again.%20Their%20father%20had%20passed%20when%20Rupam%20was%20just%2011%2C%20and%20now%2C%20within%20a%20week%20of%20being%20diagnosed%20with%20blood%20cancer%2C%20their%20mother%20too%20was%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRelatives%2C%20instead%20of%20offering%20support%2C%20distanced%20themselves.%20We%20were%20only%20two%20daughters%2C%20and%20society%20was%20cruel%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rupam%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20told%20us%20we%20had%20no%20future%2C%20that%20we%20were%20helpless%20without%20parents.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496969%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20in%20that%20moment%20of%20loss%20and%20abandonment%2C%20Rupam%20found%20the%20spark%20of%20a%20promise%20%E2%80%94%20to%20her%20mother%2C%20and%20to%20herself%3A%20%3Cem%3EI%20will%20d