ur%2C%20Mohan%20broke%20down%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20fields%20are%20gone.%20I%20know%20I%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20sow%20anything%20for%20another%20year%20until%20the%20soil%20becomes%20fertile%20again%20and%20the%20mud%20is%20removed.%20What%20am%20I%20going%20to%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-1-1757073005.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Relief%20and%20rescue%20operations%20are%20ongoing%20on%20ground%20to%20help%20the%20people%20affected%20by%20the%20Punjab%20floods%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-1-1757073005.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-1-1757073005-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-1-1757073005-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-1-1757073005-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2Fpunjab-floods-1-1757073005-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496937%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERelief%20and%20rescue%20operations%20are%20underway%20to%20support%20people%20affected%20by%20the%20Punjab%20floods.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20had%20the%20answers.%20Harmeet%20Singh%2C%20who%20leads%20CSR%20(Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility)%20at%20Kalgidhar%20Trust%2C%20admits%20that%2C%20despite%20having%20conducted%20relief%20and%20rescue%20operations%20for%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20they%20are%20daunted%20by%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20calamity%20%E2%80%94%20these%20are%20bei